s" target="_blank">详细了解引荐网址。</a>','<strong>Check this to confirm you would like to update the "Unpaid Commission", "Pending Payments", and "Processing Commission" to the above.</strong><br/>(If you leave unchecked it stays the same, incase any new commission was earned since you opened this page.)'=>'<strong>勾选此项以确认您希望将 "未支付佣金"、"待支付佣金 "和 "处理中佣金 "更新为上述内容。</strong><br/>（如果不勾选，则保持不变，以防您打开此页面后赚取了新佣金）。','<strong>Note:</strong> This setting is shared with the Registration &rsaquo; Extra Fields settings.'=>'<strong>注意：</strong>此设置与注册 &rsaquo; 额外字段设置共享。','<strong>Why is there a difference?</strong> The total commission shown is the all-time commission earned across all referred orders. However, the processing, unpaid, pending, and paid commission amounts only begin tracking from the point at which the payouts system was activated. Orders completed <em>before</em> the plugin was installed (or before the payouts feature was enabled) will contribute to the total commission figure but will not appear in the individual payout categories - resulting in this difference. <a href="https://couponaffiliates.com/docs/unpaid-commission-is-0-even-though-there-are-referred-orders/" target="_blank">Learn how to grant unpaid commission for past orders &rarr;</a>'=>'<strong>为什么会有区别？</strong>显示的总佣金是所有推荐订单的总佣金。但是，处理中、未支付、待支付和已支付的佣金金额仅从支付系统启动时开始跟踪。在安装插件<em></em>之前（或在启用支付功能之前）完成的订单将计入总佣金数字，但不会出现在单个支付类别中，因此会出现这种差异。<a href="https://couponaffiliates.com/docs/unpaid-commission-is-0-even-though-there-are-referred-orders/" target="_blank">了解如何为过去的订单发放未支付的佣金&rarr;</a>。','[%s] This is a test SMS from Coupon Affiliates. Your SMS notifications are working correctly!'=>'[%s] 这是来自 Coupon Affiliates 的测试短信。您的短信通知工作正常！','[Admin] Only the affiliate user for this coupon can setup their Stripe account connection.'=>'[管理员]只有此优惠券的联盟用户才能设置他们的 Stripe 账户连接。','[Admin] You can edit the account details for this user in the admin area: %s'=>'[管理员]您可以在管理区域中编辑此用户的帐户详细信息：%s','[Live] API Publishable Key'=>'[直播]API 可发布密钥','[Live] API Secret Key'=>'[直播]API 秘密密钥','[Live] API Token'=>'[实时] 应用程序接口令牌','[Live] Client ID'=>'[直播]客户 ID','[Live] Client Secret'=>'[直播]客户秘密','[Live] Profile ID'=>'[现场] 配置文件 ID','[Test] API Publishable Key'=>'[测试]API 可发布密钥','[Test] API Secret Key'=>'[测试]API 秘密密钥','[Test] API Token'=>'[测试] 应用程序接口令牌','[Test] Client ID'=>'[测试]客户 ID','[Test] Client Secret'=>'[测试]客户秘密','[Test] Profile ID'=>'[测试] 配置文件 ID','[Warning] You have this option enabled: Delete plugin options and custom database tables on plugin deletion. (See \'Debug\' Settings)'=>'[警告]您已启用此选项：删除插件选项和插件删除时的自定义数据库表。（请参阅“调试”设置）','[{site_name}] Affiliate registration approved for {name}.'=>'[{site_name}]已批准{name}的联盟注册。','[{site_name}] Affiliate {name} has requested a payout of {amount}. Please review.'=>'[{site_name}]联属会员{name}要求支付{金额}。请审核。','[{site_name}] Congratulations {name}! Your affiliate application has been approved. Log in to your dashboard to get started.'=>'[{site_name}] 祝贺 {name}！您的联属会员申请已获批准。登录您的控制面板开始工作。','[{site_name}] Great news, {name}! You just earned {commission} commission from a new referral sale (Order #{id}). Keep it up!'=>'[{site_name}]好消息，{name}！您刚刚从一个新的转介销售（订单 #{id}）中赚取了 {commission} 佣金。继续努力','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, unfortunately one of your referred orders (#{id}) has been {status} and the commission has been removed.'=>'[{site_name}] 你好，{name}，很遗憾，您推荐的一个订单（#{id}）已被{status}，佣金已被取消。','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, your commission payout of {amount} has been successfully processed! Thank you.'=>'[{site_name}] 嗨，{姓名}，您的佣金{金额}已成功支付！谢谢。','[{site_name}] Hi {name}, your payout request for {amount} has been received and is being processed.'=>'[{网站名称}] 嗨，{姓名}，已收到您的 {金额}赔付请求，正在处理中。','[{site_name}] New affiliate registration from {name} ({email}) is awaiting your approval.'=>'来自 {name} ({email}) 的 [{site_name}] 新联盟注册正等待您的批准。','[{site_name}] New referral sale! Affiliate {name} (coupon: {coupon}) earned {commission} commission on order #{id}.'=>'[{site_name}] 新推荐销售！联属会员 {name}（优惠券：{coupon}）从订单 #{id} 中获得 {commission} 佣金。','[{site_name}] Order #{id} by affiliate {name} has been {status}. Commission removed.'=>'[{site_name}]联属会员 {name} 的 #{id} 订单已被 {status}。佣金已取消。','[{site_name}] Payout of {amount} sent to affiliate {name} (payout #{id}).'=>'[{site_name}]向联属会员 {name} 发送了 {amount} 付款（付款 #{id}）。','A custom "manual" payment method of your choice.'=>'您选择的自定义"手动"支付方式。','A direct bank transfer payment method (paid manually).'=>'直接银行转账支付方式（手动支付）。','a discount'=>'折扣','A fixed amount earned for sub-affiliate referrals'=>'为子代理推荐赚取的固定金额','A login form will be displayed on the affiliate dashboard for users to login to their account, and directly access their dashboard without needing to use the unique link.'=>'联盟仪表板上将显示登录表单，供用户登录其帐户，并直接访问其仪表板，而无需使用唯一链接。','A new "Bonuses" tab will be shown in the affiliate dashboard displaying all the available bonuses, and their current progress towards achieving it.'=>'一个新的“奖金”选项卡将显示在会员仪表板中，显示所有可用的奖金，以及他们当前实现奖金的进度。','A new "creatives" tab will be shown in the affiliate dashboard displaying these creatives, including a HTML code for them to copy and paste, to show the banner on their own site (with the referral link).'=>'新的"创意"选项卡将显示在显示这些创意的附属仪表板中，包括用于复制和粘贴的 HTML 代码，以显示他们自己的网站上的横幅（带有推荐链接）。','A payout request will only be requested automatically if:'=>'只有在：','A shortlink will only be created once for the same URL. A shortlink can also only be created if the URL is pointing to this website'=>'短链接仅为同一 URL 创建一次。只有指向此网站，才能创建短链接','A user cannot be their own sub-affiliate.'=>'用户不能成为自己的次级会员。','A user has not yet been assigned to this coupon.'=>'尚未将用户分配给此优惠券。','A user has not yet been assigned to this coupon. (This message is only visible to admins.)'=>'尚未将用户分配到此优惠券。（此消息仅对管理员可见。','Ability automatically collect the latest conversion rates for currencies, and update them automatically in the multi-currency settings.'=>'能够自动收集货币的最新兑换率，并在多币种设置中自动更新它们。','Ability to link a landing page to an affiliate coupon, which will then work the same as a referral URL.'=>'能够将着