款）。','Allow administrator users to fill out the registration form for new users.'=>'允许管理员用户填写新用户的注册表。','Allow affiliate user to apply their own coupon code at cart / checkout.'=>'允许联盟用户在购物车/结账时应用自己的优惠券代码。','Allow affiliates to enter a custom payout amount.'=>'允许联盟成员输入自定义收款金额。','Allow affiliates to opt out of SMS notifications'=>'允许联属会员选择退出短信通知','Allow affiliates to upload their invoice when requesting a payout for their unpaid commission.'=>'允许关联公司在申请支付未付佣金时上传其发票。','Allow logged out users to register as an affiliate.'=>'允许注销的用户注册联盟优惠券。','Allow MLA parent to approve/decline their sub-affiliate registrations.'=>'允许工作重点家长批准/取消其子会员注册。','Allow multiple affiliate coupons to be used in the same order.'=>'允许以相同顺序使用多个附属优惠券。','Allow the affiliate to upload an invoice (PDF file) when requesting a payout.'=>'允许关联公司在请求付款时上传发票 （PDF 文件）。','Allow your affiliates to create referral "campaigns" and then create custom URLs to track clicks/conversions per campaign.'=>'允许您的关联公司创建转介"活动"，然后创建自定义网市来跟踪每个广告活动的点击/转换。','Allow your affiliates to request commission payouts as "Store Credit" which they can use towards purchases in your store at checkout.'=>'允许您的关联公司申请佣金支付作为"商店信用"，他们可以用于在结账时在您的商店购买。','Allow your affiliates to request commission payouts via Wise Bank Transfer.'=>'允许您的联属会员通过 Wise Bank Transfer（明智银行转账）申请佣金支付。','Allows you to set custom commission rates per user role. This will replace the settings set above, if it is set.'=>'允许您为每个用户角色设置自定义佣金率。如果已设置，这将替换上面设置的设置。','All‑time total commission earned'=>'历年赚取的佣金总额','All‑time total order value attributed (minus discounts if tracked)'=>'归属的所有时间订单总价值（如果已跟踪，则减去折扣）','All‑time total referrals (uses coupon usage count)'=>'历年推荐人总数（使用优惠券使用计数）','Also block MANUAL use of affiliate coupons, if referred by a blocked domain.'=>'此外，如果被阻止的域引用，请阻止手动使用联盟优惠券。','Alt Text:'=>'替代文本：','Alternatively, enable the option below to disable this field and generate a specific code automatically via a merge tag template.'=>'或者，启用以下选项以禁用此字段，并通过合并标签模板自动生成特定代码。','Alternatively, you can add the %s shortcode to a new page, then select the page from the dropdown below.'=>'或者，您也可以将 %s 短代码添加到新页面，然后从下面的下拉菜单中选择页面。','Alternatively, you can allow affiliates to register as an affiliate. When accepted, this will then automatically create the coupon and assign them to it.'=>'或者，您可以允许附属公司注册为附属公司。接受后，这将自动创建优惠券并将其分配给它。','Always Enabled'=>'始终启用','always on'=>'总是','Amount'=>'量','Amount of orders to show on the affiliate dashboard by default.'=>'默认情况下，要在会员仪表板上显示的订单数量。','An %1$s application has been submitted for user "{username}" for the coupon "{coupon}".'=>'用户"{username}"已为优惠券"{coupon}"提交了 %1$s 申请。','An active affiliate is any user with at least one coupon assigned to them, and not unsubscribed from newsletter emails.'=>'活跃联属会员是指至少有一张优惠券的用户，且未退订时事通讯电子邮件。','An error occurred when attempting to reverse the Stripe payment.'=>'尝试撤销 Stripe 付款时出错。','An error occurred when attempting to send the Stripe payment.'=>'尝试发送 Stripe 付款时出错。','An error occurred when attempting to send the Stripe payment. Please check your Stripe account.'=>'尝试发送 Stripe 付款时出错。请检查您的 Stripe 帐户。','An error occurred while generating URL.'=>'生成 URL 时发生错误。','An error occurred while getting coupon code.'=>'获取优惠券代码时发生错误。','An error occurred while getting coupon description.'=>'获取优惠券描述时发生错误。','An error occurred while getting dashboard URL.'=>'获取仪表板 URL 时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading content.'=>'加载内容时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading creatives.'=>'加载创意时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading custom tab 1.'=>'加载自定义选项卡 1 时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading custom tab 2.'=>'加载自定义选项卡 2 时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading links.'=>'加载链接时出现错误。','An error occurred while loading payouts.'=>'加载付款时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading referrals.'=>'加载推荐时发生错误。','An error occurred while loading statistics.'=>'加载统计数据时发生错误。','and add or edit a coupon, then assign users under the "coupon affiliates" tab'=>'并添加或编辑优惠券，然后在 “优惠券联盟” 选项卡下分配用户','and view the group ID here:'=>'并在此处查看组 ID：','Animation Type:'=>'动画类型：','Any Status'=>'任何状态','API Key'=>'API 密钥','API URL'=>'API 网址','APILayer API Key'=>'APILayer API Key','apilayer.com'=>'apilayer.com','Applies to all text in the Affiliate Portal. Fonts available from the <a href="%s" target="_blank">WordPress Font Library</a>.'=>'适用于联盟门户中的所有文本。字体可从<a href="%s" target="_blank">WordPress字体库</a>获取。','Apply'=>'申请','Apply %s credit to this order.'=>'将 %s 信用额度应用于此订单。','Apply restrictions on when affiliate coupons can be used to help prevent affiliate fraud.'=>'限制何时可以使用联盟优惠券来帮助防止联盟欺诈。','Are shipping costs excluded from stats and calculations?'=>'运费是否不包括在统计和计算中？','Are you sure you want to cancel this Wise Bank Transfer payout? This will also attempt to cancel the transfer in your Wise account if it has been created and return the commission to unpaid balance.'=>'您确定要取消这笔慧科银行转账付款吗？如果已在您的 Wise 账户中创建转账，此操作也将尝试取消该转账，并将佣金返还至未支付余额。','Are you sure you want to decline this application?'=>'您确定要拒绝这项申请吗？','Are you sure you want to delete all these registration entries?'=>'您确定要删除所有这些注册条目吗？','Are you sure you want to delete the'=>'您确定要删除','Are you sure you want to delete the selected coupons AND their assigned affiliate users? This will also delete all coupons belonging to those users and permanently remove their user accounts.'=>'您确定要删除所选优惠券及其指定的联盟用户吗？这也会删除属于这些用户的所有优惠券，并永久删除他们的用户账户。','Are you sure you want to delete the selected coupons?'=>'您确定要删除所选优惠券吗？','Are you sure you want to delete this coupon?'=>'您确定要删除此优惠券吗？','Are you sure you want to delete this role?'=>'是否确实要删除此角色？','Are you sure you want to refresh all this coupons affiliate dashboard data? The next time you visit the affiliate dashboard, it may take significantly longer to load (first visit).'=>'您确定要刷新所有这些优惠券联盟仪表板数据吗？下次您访问联属营销控制面板时，加载时间可能会明显延长（首次访问）。','Are you sure you want to refresh the affiliate stats for this order? This will delete the current referral stats/commission and recalculate them.'=>'您确定要刷新此订单的联盟统计数据吗？这将删除当前的推荐统计数据/佣金并重新计算它们。','Are you sure you want to remove this coupon from the order?'=>'您确定要从订单中删除此优惠券吗？','Are you sure you want to unassign the selected affiliates from these coupons? This will remove the affiliate assignment but will NOT delete coupons or users.'=>'您确定要从这些优惠券中取消指定选定的联属会员吗？这将删除联属会员分配，但不会删除优惠券或用户。','as a template and enter the exact name of it below.'=>'作为模板，并在下面输入其确切名称。','As an admin, you can also manually add new affiliate registrations easily in the "Registrations" admin page, via the "Create New Registration" button.'=>'作为管理员，您还可以通过"创建新注册"按钮在"注册"管理页面中轻松手动添加新的联盟注册。','As an admin, you can then easily download/view the invoice in the admin "Payouts" list, found under a new "Files" column, before completing the payout.'=>'作为管理员，您可以在完成付款之前轻松下载/查看管理员"付款"列表中的发票，该列表在新的"文件"列下找到。','as normal in WooCommerce. You can then assign affiliate users to these coupons (see below) to make them an affiliate.'=>'在WooCommerce中正常。然后，您可以将联盟用户分配给这些优惠券（见下文），以使其成为联盟会员。','As the parent affiliate, they will then earn a percentage of extra commission for all sales that their sub-affiliates refer to you.'=>'作为母附属公司，他们将为其子附属公司推荐给您的所有销售赚取一定比例的额外佣金。','Assign Affiliates to Coupons'=>'将附属公司分配给优惠券','Assign affiliates to groups and then configure a variety of settings for that whole group.'=>'将 Affiliates 分配给组，然后为整个组配置各种设置。','Assign Orders to %s'=>'将订单分配给 %s','Assign Role/Group'=>'指定角色/组别','Assign this landing page to an affiliate coupon. Enter the exact coupon code.'=>'将此登录页面分配给联盟优惠券。输入确切的优惠券代码。','Assign to a new user role or affiliate group'=>'分配给新的用户角色或关联组','Assign to role:'=>'分配给角色：','Assign user roles (groups) to specific templates'=>'将用户角色（组）分配给特定模板','Assigning a landing page to a coupon will act in the same way as a referral URL (click tracking and auto assign coupon).'=>'将着陆页分配给优惠券将以与转介 URL 相同的方式工作（单击跟踪和自动分配优惠券）。','at'=>'在','Attempt to apply coupon instantly on first page visited.'=>'尝试在访问的第一页立即应用优惠券。','Attribution Model'=>'归因模型','Audience ID'=>'受众 ID','Australia'=>'澳大利亚','Austria'=>'奥地利','Auth Token:'=>'认证令牌：','Auto Apply Coupon'=>'自动申请优惠券','Auto Apply Coupon to Cart'=>'自动将优惠券应用到购物车','Auto-Accept Registrations'=>'自动接受注册','Auto-assign referred customers as an MLA sub-affiliate.'=>'自动将推荐的客户分配为 MLA 子关联。','Automated Conversion Rates'=>'自动转换率','Automatic Affiliate Registration'=>'自动联盟注册','Automatic encryption/decryption handling for bank details'=>'对大多数银行信息进行自动加密/解密处理。','Automatic Payouts'=>'自动付款','Automatic Saving (AJAX)'=>'自动保存（AJAX）','Automatically accept all affiliate registrations.'=>'自动接受所有联营注册申请。','Automatically add unpaid commission a number of days after completion (optional).'=>'在完成后数天自动添加未付佣金（可选）。','Automatically apply coupon to cart/checkout if referral URL is used.'=>'如果使用转介 URL，请自动将优惠券应用于推车/结账。','Automatically apply the coupon to the customer\'s cart when they click the action button (if not already applied).'=>'当顾客点击操作按钮时，自动将优惠券应用到购物车（如果尚未应用）。','Automatically generate a PDF statement when your affiliates request a commission payout.'=>'当您的关联公司请求佣金支付时，自动生成 PDF 报表。','Automatically log the user in after registration.'=>'用户注册后自动登录。','Automatically pay your affiliates in one-click with PayPal Payouts! Your affiliates get paid instantly directly from your account.'=>'自动支付您的附属公司一键与PayPal支付！您的关联公司会立即从您的帐户获得报酬。','Automatically pay your affiliates in one-click with Stripe! Your affiliates get paid instantly directly from your Stripe funds.'=>'自动支付您的附属公司一键与条纹！您的附属公司会立即从您的条纹基金获得直接报酬。','Automatically register all new users as an affiliate.'=>'自动将所有新用户注册为联盟会员。','Automatically send an email report (and PDF) to affiliates every week/month with a summary of their recent commission and referral stats.'=>'每周/每月自动向关联公司发送电子邮件报告（和 PDF），并汇总其最近的佣金和推荐统计数据。','Automatically send an email report (with an attached PDF report) to affiliates every week/month with a summary of their recent referral/commission stats.'=>'每周/每月自动向联盟成员发送电子邮件报告（附带 PDF 报告），其中包含他们最近的推荐/佣金统计数据的摘要。','Automatically submit "payout requests" for your affiliates, every month, week or day, if they meet certain criteria.'=>'每月、每周或每