iates - MLA Commission'=>'优惠券附属公司 - MLA 佣金','Coupon Affiliates - MLA Dashboard'=>'优惠券附属公司 - MLA 仪表板','Coupon Affiliates - MLA Parent Users'=>'优惠券附属公司 - MLA 家长用户','Coupon Affiliates - MLA Per-User Tier Commission Rates'=>'优惠券联盟 - MLA 每用户层级佣金率','Coupon Affiliates - Payment Settings'=>'优惠券联盟 - 支付设置','Coupon Affiliates - Store Credit'=>'优惠券联盟 - 商店积分','Coupon Affiliates enhances affiliate marketing by integrating coupons as a core feature. Unlike traditional affiliate systems that rely primarily on referral links, this plugin allows affiliates to share their unique coupon codes. These codes not only track sales for commission purposes but also offer customers immediate discounts or special offers, enriching the purchasing experience. However, the Coupon Affiliates system still maintains the flexibility of referral links; affiliates can share URLs that automatically apply their coupon at checkout, and even if a coupon isn\'t used, you can <a href="%s" target="_blank">still make the link alone track referrals</a>, ensuring affiliates receive credit for every sale referred.'=>'Coupon Affiliates 通过将优惠券集成为核心功能来增强联盟营销。与主要依赖推荐链接的传统会员系统不同，此插件允许会员分享他们独特的优惠券代码。这些代码不仅可以跟踪销售以达到佣金目的，还可以为客户提供即时折扣或特别优惠，从而丰富购买体验。但是，优惠券会员系统仍然保持推荐链接的灵活性;会员可以共享在结账时自动应用优惠券的 URL，即使没有使用优惠券，您 <a href="%s" target="_blank">仍然可以单独使用链接跟踪</a>推荐，确保会员收到推荐的每笔销售的信用。','Coupon Affiliates for WooCommerce (PRO)'=>'伍商业的优惠券联盟 （PRO）','Coupon Affiliates: Activity Log'=>'优惠券关联公司 - 活动日志','Coupon Affiliates: Creatives'=>'优惠券联盟 - 创意','Coupon Affiliates: Email Newsletters'=>'优惠券联盟：电子邮件通讯','Coupon Affiliates: Info & Help'=>'优惠券联盟 - 信息和帮助','Coupon Affiliates: PRO Modules'=>'优惠券联盟 - PRO 模块','Coupon Affiliates: Setup Wizard'=>'优惠券关联公司 - 设置向导','Coupon Affiliates: Short URLs'=>'优惠券联盟 - 短 URL','Coupon Affiliates: Statements'=>'优惠券联盟 - 声明','Coupon applied successfully!'=>'优惠券已成功应用！','Coupon Checkout Settings'=>'优惠券结帐设置','Coupon Code'=>'优惠券代码','Coupon code already exists: '=>'优惠券代码已存在：','Coupon code successfully created:'=>'成功创建优惠券代码：','Cou