知','Enable some more advanced affiliate registration features such as custom form fields, multiple templates, dynamic code generator, auto accept, auto registration, and more.'=>'启用一些更高级的联盟注册功能，例如自定义表单字段，动态代码生成器，自动接受，自动注册等。','Enable terms and conditions checkbox on registration form.'=>'启用注册表上的条款和条件复选框。','Enable Test Mode?'=>'启用测试模式？','Enable the "Additional Email Addresses" field in affiliate settings.'=>'在联盟设置中启用"其他电子邮件地址"字段。','Enable this to automatically submit "payout requests" for your affiliates, every month/week/day, if they meet certain criteria.'=>'如果关联公司符合某些标准，则可每月/每周/每天自动提交"付款请求"。','Enable this to only link customer to coupon as "lifetime referral" if the coupon has a user affiliate assigned to it.'=>'如果优惠券有指定用户关联，则仅将客户与优惠券链接为"终身推荐"。','Enabled'=>'启用','Enabling this option will enable lifetime commission for ALL your affiliates & coupons. You can alternatively enable lifetime commission on a per-coupon basis, in the individual coupon settings.'=>'启用此选项将启用所有附属公司和优惠券的终身佣金。您也可以在单个优惠券设置中，按每票单设置启用终身佣金。','Enabling this option will prevent ALL affiliate coupons and referral links from working UNLESS the customer was directly linked by the approved domain that is assigned to that coupon.'=>'启用此选项将阻止所有优惠券和推荐链接正常工作，除非客户由分配给该优惠券的批准域直接链接。','Enabling this will allow the unique coupon affiliate dashboard URLs to be used without the ID, but both URLs will still work.'=>'启用此功能将允许在没有 ID 的情况下使用唯一的优惠券联盟仪表板 URL，但这两个 URL 仍然有效。','End'=>'结束','End Date:'=>'结束日期：','Ensure you have setup your billing details, added credit to your balance, and enabled low balance notifications. Keep your credentials secure and monitor your balance usage.'=>'确保您已设置账单详情、为余额添加信用额度并启用余额不足通知。确保密码安全并监控余额使用情况。','Enter a coupon code to preview'=>'输入优惠券代码进行预览','Enter a custom commission "fixed amount per product" for this product category.'=>'为该产品类别输入自定义佣金 "每件产品固定金额"。','Enter a custom commission percentage for this product category.'=>'输入该产品类别的自定义佣金百分比。','Enter an email address.'=>'输入电子邮件地址。','Enter in international format, e.g. +447911123456. Leave blank to disable SMS notifications.'=>'以国际格式输入，例如 +447911123456。留空表示禁用短信通知。','Enter minimum payout amount (e.g., "$5.00")'=>'输入最低收款金额（例如，“$5.00”）','Enter one per line.'=>'每行输入一个。','Enter one per line. You do not need to include "http://", "https://", or "www." in the domain.'=>'每行输入一个。您无需在域中包含"http://"、"https://"或"www."。','Enter page URL...'=>'输入页面 URL...','Enter payment methods (e.g., "PayPal, Bank Transfer, or Stripe")'=>'输入付款方式（例如，“PayPal、银行转账或 Stripe”）','Enter the commission rate (e.g., "25%" or "$10 per sale")'=>'输入佣金率（例如，“25%”或“每次销售 10 美元”）','Enter the ID of a user here. Useful if you want to limit this bonus to a specific user.'=>'在此处输入用户的 ID。如果您想将此奖金限制为特定用户，则很有用。','Enter the name of the coupon code that will be created.'=>'输入将要创建的优惠券代码名称。','Enter the title for the affiliate program page'=>'输入联盟计划页面的标题','Enter the URL slug for the affiliate program page (e.g., "affiliate-program")'=>'输入联属计划页面的 URL slug（例如，“affiliate-program”）','Enter URLs separated by commas. Use relative URLs (e.g., /shop, /about) or full URLs. Use * for wildcards (e.g., /shop/* for all shop pages).'=>'输入用逗号分隔的 URL。使用相对 URL（如/shop、/about）或完整 URL。使用 * 表示通配符（例如，/shop/* 表示所有商店页面）。','Enter user email address...'=>'输入用户电子邮件地址...','Enter your Address Line 1 to show on statements.'=>'输入地址行 1 以显示对帐单。','Enter your Address Line 2 to show on statements.'=>'输入地址行 2 以显示对帐单。','Enter your city, state and ZIP/postal code to show on statements.'=>'输入您的城市、州和邮政编码，以显示在报表上。','Enter your commission amounts below (0 to disable). If you enter multiple types, they will be combined. For example you could have: 10% of total order, plus an extra $2 per product.'=>'输入以下佣金金额（0 到禁用）。如果您输入多种类型，它们将被组合在一起。例如，您可以拥有：总订单的 10%，外加每种产品的额外 2 美元。','Enter your Company Name to show on statements.'=>'输入您的公司名称以显示对账单。','Enter your domain...'=>'输入您的域名...','Enter your terms acceptance message. Make sure you edit the message to include links to your terms and privacy policy!'=>'输入您的条款接受信息。请确保您链接编辑的消息，以包括链接到您的条款和隐私政策！','Enter your VAT/Tax number to show on statements.'=>'输入您的增值税/税号以显示对账单。','Equal'=>'平等','Equal or Less'=>'等于或少于','Equal or More'=>'等于或更多','Equal or More than'=>'等于或大于','Error'=>'错误','Error cancelling transfer: '=>'错误取消传输：','Error checking transfer status: '=>'错误检查传输状态：','Error checking username.'=>'用户名检查出错。','Error creating coupon.'=>'创建优惠券出错。','Error creating recipient account: '=>'创建收件人帐户出错：','Error loading content. Please try again.'=>'加载内容时出错。请重试。','Error loading creatives.'=>'加载创意时出错。','Error loading links.'=>'链接加载出错。','Error loading payouts.'=>'加载赔款时出错。','Error loading referrals.'=>'加载推荐信息时出错。','Error loading statistics.'=>'加载统计数据出错。','Error updating user.'=>'更新用户时出错。','Error: Bank details not provided. Please set up your bank account information first.'=>'错误：未提供银行详细信息。请先设置您的银行账户信息。','Error: Could not create recipient account for bank transfer. Please check your bank details.'=>'错误：无法为银行转账创建收款账户。请检查您的银行详细信息。','Error: Could not retrieve transfer status from Wise.'=>'错误：无法从 Wise 获取传输状态。','Error: Coupon does not exist.'=>'错误：优惠券不存在。','Error: Currency not supported by Wise API. Currency:'=>'错误：Wise API 不支持货币。货币：','Error: Failed to find the table %s'=>'错误：查找 %s 表失败','ERROR: Failed to load ajax request. Session may have timed out. Refresh the page to try again.'=>'错误：加载 ajax 请求失败。会话可能超时。刷新页面重试。','Error: For PayPal Payouts, please enter your PayPal API Credentials in the'=>'错误：对于 PayPal 支付，请在','Error: For Stripe Payouts, please enter your Stripe API Credentials in the'=>'错误：对于 Stripe 付款，请在','Error: For Wise Bank Transfer Payouts, please enter your Wise API Credentials in the'=>'错误：对于慧科银行转账支付，请在','Error: Invalid bank details format. Please provide complete bank account information.'=>'错误：银行详细信息格式无效。请提供完整的银行账户信息。','Error: No payout methods are enabled. Please go to %sPayouts Settings%s and enable at-least one payout method.'=>'错误：未启用任何付款方式。请转到 %sPayouts Settings%s 并至少启用一种付款方式。','Error: No transfer ID provided.'=>'错误：未提供传输 ID。','Error: Wise Profile ID not configured. Please check your Wise API settings.'=>'错误：未配置 Wise 配置文件 ID。请检查您的 Wise API 设置。','Estimated send time ~ %d seconds (based on 2s delay).'=>'预计发送时间 ~ %d 秒（基于 2 秒延迟）。','Estonia'=>'爱沙尼亚','EU IBAN accounts → Receive EUR (converted from your store currency)'=>'欧盟 IBAN 账户 → 接收欧元（从您的商店货币转换而来）','European Union (IBAN)'=>'欧洲联盟（IBAN）','Even if the "coupon code" isnt used, the commission and sales will still be tracked on the coupons affiliate dashboard. All future orders by that customer, even with different coupon codes, will only apply to the original coupon affiliate.'=>'即使没有使用"优惠券代码"，佣金和销售仍将在优惠券附属仪表板上跟踪。该客户的所有未来订单，即使具有不同的优惠券代码，也仅适用于原始优惠券关联公司。','Event'=>'事件','Every: Display every time the referral URL parameter is present'=>'每次每次出现推荐 URL 参数时都会显示','Example default referral URL with coupon code "example" would be'=>'优惠券代码为“example”的默认推荐 URL 示例为','Example URL with campaign "twitter" would be'=>'示例 URL 与活动 "推特" 将是','Example URL with user "example" would be'=>'带有用户“示例”的示例网址将是','Exchange rates will be updated automatically every 12 hours, or you can click the button below to update it now.'=>'汇率将每 12 小时自动更新一次，或者您可以单击下面的按钮立即更新。','Exchangerates API Key'=>'汇率 API 密钥','exchangeratesapi.io'=>'exchangeratesapi.io','Exclude Sale Items'=>'排除特价商品','Exclude/Remove taxes from Store Credit in cart.'=>'从购物车中的商店信用额中排除/移除税费','Expiration Date:'=>'有效期：','Expires'=>'到期','Expiry Date'=>'有效期','Export'=>'出口','Export %s Users'=>'导出 %s 用户','Export Orders'=>'出口订单','Export Orders (PRO)'=>'出口订单 (PRO)','Export Orders is available in PRO.'=>'专业版中提供导出订单功能。','Export Payouts'=>'出口付款','Export Payouts (PRO)'=>'出口支付 (PRO)','Export Payouts is available in PRO.'=>'专业版中提供导出付款功能。','Export to Excel Buttons'=>'出口到 Excel 按钮','External URL:'=>'外部 URL：','Extra features are available with PRO version including custom commission amounts per coupon, email notifications, and more. <a href="%s">UPGRADE</a>'=>'PRO 版本提供额外的功能，包括每张优惠券的自定义佣金金额、电子邮件通知等。 <a href="%s">升级</a>','Extra Field Label'=>'额外字段标签','Extra Fields'=>'额外字段','Extra Restrictions'=>'额外限制','Extra Settings'=>'额外设置','Fade In'=>'淡入','Failed to copy'=>'复制失败','Failed to create the page.'=>'创建页面失败。','Fees vary (typically around 1% - 2%). Learn more about Stripe Connect'=>'费用各不相同（通常约为 1% - 2%）。了解有关条纹连接的更多情况','Fetch Profiles'=>'获取简介','Field'=>'现场','Field Label:'=>'字段标签：','Files'=>'文件','Filter'=>'滤波器','Filter by'=>'过滤器由','Filter by Payment Method'=>'按付款方式筛选','Filter by Status'=>'按状态筛选','Filter by user roles/groups:'=>'根据用户角色/组进行筛选：','Filtered by user roles:'=>'按用户角色筛选：','Finally, we need to setup the email notifications for your affiliate program.'=>'最后，我们需要为您的联盟计划设置电子邮件通知。','Find these in your <a href="https://console.twilio.com/" target="_blank">Twilio Console</a> dashboard.'=>'在<a href="https://console.twilio.com/" target="_blank">Twilio控制台</a>仪表板中查找这些内容。','Finish'=>'完成','Finland'=>'芬兰','First & Last Name Required'=>'名字和姓氏必填','First Name'=>'名字','First visit - this will take a little longer than usual.'=>'首次就诊--这将比平时花费更多时间。','First-Click Attribution'=>'首次点击归因','First-Click: Once a referral cookie exists, later referral links won’t replace it or the cart coupon automatically; customers can still manually apply a different coupon.'=>'首次点击：一旦存在推介 cookie，以后的推介链接不会自动替换它或购物车优惠券；客户仍可手动应用不同的优惠券。','Firstly, if you have not already, get started by creating a new page and adding the shortcode: [couponaffiliates-register]'=>'首先，如果您还没有，请先创建一个新页面并添加简码： [couponaffiliates-register]','Firstly, we need to create the main affiliate dashboard page on your website.'=>'首先，我们需要在您的网站上创建主要的联盟仪表板页面。','Fixed'=>'固定','Fixed Amount'=>'固定金额','Fixed Amount ($)'=>'固定金额 （$）','Fixed amount on cart.'=>'车上的固定金额。','Fixed Amount Per Order'=>'每个订单的固定金额','Fixed Amount Per Product'=>'每个产品的固定金额','Fixed amount you earn per sub-affiliate referral.'=>'每推荐一名次级会员可获得固定金额。','Fixed Cart Discount'=>'固定购物车折扣','Fixed cart discount'=>'固定购物车折扣','Fixed Commission (%s - Amount Per Order)'=>'固定佣金 （%s - 每笔订单的金额）','Fixed Commission (%s - Amount Per Product)'=>'固定佣金 （%s - 每件产品的金额）','Fixed Commission Per Order'=>'每笔订单固定佣金','Fixed Commission Per Product'=>'每个产品的固定佣金','Fixed discount on subscription signup.'=>'订阅注册的固定折扣。','Fixed Product Discount'=>'固定产品折扣','Fixed product discount'=>'固定产品折扣','Flexible Commission - Per Product or Coupon'=>'灵活佣金 - 每个产品或优惠券','Flexible Commission Settings'=>'灵活的佣金设置','Flexible commission settings can also be set at product level, as well as coupon level. To do this, simply edit a product, or coupon, and visit the "Coupon Affiliates & Commission" data settings tab.'=>'灵活的佣金设置也可以设置在产品级别以及优惠券级别。要做到这一点，只需编辑产品或优惠券，并访问"优惠券联盟和佣金"数据设置选项卡。','Floating Affiliate Widget'=>'浮动联盟小工具','Floating Button Colors'=>'浮动按钮颜色','Floating Widget'=>'浮动小工具','Footer Text'=>'页脚文本','For "unpaid commission" to be granted (PRO), the order status must be "completed".'=>'要授予 "未付佣金"（PRO），订单状态必须为 "已完成"。','for a solution.'=>'对于某些解决方案。','For advanced features like automated payouts, multi-level affiliates, dynamic creatives, performance bonuses, affiliate groups, email reports, and more, visit the <a href="%s" target="_blank">PRO modules section</a>.'=>'有关自动付款、多级联属会员、动态创意、业绩奖金、联属会员组、电子邮件报告等高级功能，请访问 <a href="%s" target="_blank">专业模块部分</a>。','For affiliate registrations to work properly, you will need to create a "template coupon" and assign it in the "registration" settings tab.'=>'要使联盟注册正常工作，您需要创建一个“模板优惠券”并在设置中分配它。','For detailed information regarding the payouts features, and setting up one-click payout methods such as Stripe and PayPal,'=>'有关支付功能的详细信息，以及设置单击支付方法（如条纹和PayPal）','For example, if you want to change it to "Partner", you would enter "Partner" here. It will then change things like "Affiliate Dashboard" to "Partner Dashboard", "Affiliate Registration" to "Partner Registration", etc.'=>'例如，如果您想将其更改为 "合作伙伴"，则可在此处输入 "合作伙伴"。这样，"联属会员控制面板 "就会更改为 "合作伙伴控制面板"，"联属会员注册 "也会更改为 "合作伙伴注册 "等。','For logged-in affiliates, it shows their dashboard with statistics, referral links, recent orders, payouts, and creatives.'=>'对于已登录的联属会员，它会显示他们的仪表板，包括统计数据、推荐链接、最近的订单、付款和创意。','For more in-depth tutorials and guides, see our plugin documentation:'=>'有关更深入的教程和指南，请参阅我们的插件文档：','For more information, please see the video below:'=>'有关更多信息，请观看下面的视频：','For more information, watch the video:'=>'更多信息，请观看视频：','For most websites, the settings on this page can be ignored (keep them as they are).'=>'对于大多数网站，此页面上的设置可能会被忽略（保持它们的样数）。','For most websites, unless you are already using a 3rd party wallet plugin, we would suggest just using our free built-in wallet system.'=>'对于大多数网站，除非您已经在使用第三方钱包插件，否则我们建议您只使用我们的免费内置钱包系统。','For non-affiliates, it shows an affiliate registration form with program benefits.'=>'对于非联属会员，它将显示联属会员注册表，并提供计划优惠。','For optimal performance, please ensure the image is optimised before uploading. The maximum image width is 2000px and the maximum file size is 1MB.'=>'为获得最佳性能，请在上传前确保图像已优化。图片最大宽度为 2000px，最大文件大小为 1MB。','For this to show, a user/affiliate account must be assigned to that coupon. The tab is only shown to this user.'=>'要显示此，必须将用户/联营帐户分配到该优惠券。选项卡仅显示给此用户。','For Wise bank transfer payouts, it will automatically complete the first step of creating the unfunded payment in Wise ready to complete manually.'=>'对于 Wise 银行转账付款，它将自动完成在 Wise 中创建未备资金付款的第一步，以便手动完成。','Form CAPTCHA - Spam Protection'=>'表格验证码 - 垃圾邮件防护','Form ID'=>'表单 ID','Form Style'=>'表单样式','Form Submission'=>'表格提交','Form Visibility Settings'=>'表单可见性设置','Format'=>'格式','Format:'=>'格式：','France'=>'法国','Fraud Prevention'=>'预防欺诈','Fraud Prevention & Usage Restrictions'=>'欺诈预防和使用限制','Free Product Order'=>'免费订购产品','Free Shipping'=>'免费送货','free shipping'=>'免费送货','free shipping discount'=>'免运费折扣','Free version can display reports for up to the past 1 month.'=>'免费版本可以显示长达 4 周的报告。','Free Version:'=>'免费版：','Frequency'=>'频率','Frequency:'=>'频率：','Frequently Asked Questions:'=>'经常问的问题：','From'=>'来自','From Email Address:'=>'从电子邮件地址：','From Name:'=>'从名称：','From Phone Number (E.164 format, e.g. +15551234567):'=>'发件人电话号码（E.164 格式，例如 +15551234567）：','From:'=>'来自','Full Name'=>'全名','Funds converted and being sent'=>'资金已转换并正在发送','funds have been added back to your Stripe account, and to the affiliates unpaid commission total.'=>'资金已加回您的 Stripe 账户，以及联盟会员未支付的佣金总额。','Funds refunded'=>'退还资金','General'=>'常规','General Email Settings'=>'常规电子邮件设置','General error: '=>'一般错误：','General Questions'=>'一般问题','General Settings'=>'一般设置','Generally there should not be any reason to turn these off, but it is here just incase, and for debugging.'=>'一般来说，不应该有任何理由关闭这些，但它在这里只是万一，并调试。','Generate'=>'生成','Generate & Edit Terms and Conditions'=>'生成和编辑条款和条件','Generate a dynamic coupon name automatically.'=>'自动生成动态优惠券名称。','Generate a new admin report'=>'生成新的管理报告','Generate a signup promo page that includes your program details and the registration form.'=>'生成一个注册促销页面，其中包含您的计划详细信息和注册表。','Generate and edit the Terms & Conditions page for your affiliate program.'=>'生成并编辑您的联盟计划的条款和条件页面。','Generate and send an example report to yourself, with the settings/customisations you have set above.'=>'生成并发送示例报告给自己，上面设置设置/自定义。','Generate Coupon'=>'生成优惠券','Generate Dashboard Page'=>'生成仪表板页面','Generate New Promo Page'=>'生成新的 Promo 页面','GENERATE NEW REPORT'=>'生成新报告','Generate Promo Page'=>'生成促销页面','Generate Registration Page'=>'生成注册页面','GENERATE REPORT'=>'生成报告','Generate some advanced detailed reports and analytics for your affiliate program.'=>'为您的联盟计划生成一些高级详细报告和分析。','Generating Report'=>'生成报告','Generating...'=>'生成...','Germany'=>'德国','Get 25% Off + Free Trial'=>'七五折优惠 + 免费试用','Get priority support, and your suggestions will have more priority for development.'=>'获得优先支持，您的建议将具有更优先的发展。','Get Rates'=>'获取费率','GetResponse'=>'获取响应','Getting Started'=>'开始','Gift'=>'礼物','Gift Box'=>'礼品盒','Gift Coupon'=>'礼品券','Give affiliates extra commission % as a bonus for selecting Store Credit as their payout method.'=>'为联盟会员提供额外的佣金百分比，作为选择商店信用额作为其支付方式的奖金。','Give unpaid commission to affiliate.'=>'向会员提供未付佣金。','Give your affiliates bonuses when they reach certain goals, such as some bonus commission once they reach a certain amount of sales.'=>'当您的会员达到某些目标时，给他们奖金，例如一旦达到一定数量的销售额，就会获得一些奖金佣金。','Give your affiliates lifetime commission for ALL future purchases from all their referred users.'=>'为您的附属公司提供从其所有推荐用户购买的所有未来购买的终身佣金。','Global'=>'全球','Go to Bonuses Settings'=>'转到奖金设置','Go to Newsletter Settings'=>'转到时事通讯设置','Go to Page'=>'转到页面','Go to Payouts Settings'=>'转到付款设置','Go to Referral Links Settings'=>'转到推荐链接设置','Go to Settings'=>'前往 设置','Go to settings'=>'前往设置','Go to Tabs Settings'=>'转到选项卡设置','Go to the'=>'转到','Go to the <a href="%s" target="_blank">Add New Affiliate</a> page to add new affiliates here, which will automatically generate the coupon code for them.'=>'前往 <a href="%s" target="_blank">添加新会员</a> 页面在此处添加新的会员，这将自动生成他们的优惠券代码。','Google reCAPTCHA'=>'谷歌回顾','Gravatar.com'=>'Gravatar.com','Great! Double-check the SMTP plugin is fully configured (SPF, DKIM, DMARC, correct from email) for optimal deliverability before bulk sending.'=>'很好！在批量发送之前，请仔细检查 SMTP 插件是否已完全配置（SPF、DKIM、DMARC、正确的电子邮件），以获得最佳的发送效果。','Great! Ensure it is fully configured (auth keys / SPF & DKIM records) for best newsletter deliverability.'=>'太好了！确保已完全配置（认证密钥/SPF 和 DKIM 记录），以获得最佳的时事通讯交付能力。','Group'=>'组别','Group / Role'=>'组 / 角色','Group Display Name'=>'组显示名称','Group does not exist.'=>'组 不存在。','Group ID'=>'组 ID','Group updated successfully.'=>'组更新成功。','Groups'=>'组别','Guest'=>'游客','Handshake'=>'握手','has been paid into your connected Stripe account.'=>'已支付到您连接的 Stripe 帐户。','has been paid to'=>'已支付给','has been reversed.'=>'已被反转。','Heart'=>'心脏','Help & Support'=>'帮助与支持','Help Area'=>'帮助区域','Help Documentation'=>'帮助文档','Here is a video guide explaining how to get started with the plugin'=>'这是一个视频指南，说明如何开始使用插件','Here\'s some of the next steps you can take:'=>'以下是您可以采取的一些后续步骤：','Hi {first_name}, Congratulations, you have just earned a reward! View your affiliate dashboard for more details.'=>'嗨{first_name}，恭喜你，<br/><br/>你刚刚获得了奖励！<br/><br/>查看您的会员仪表板以获取更多详细信息。','Hidden'=>'隐藏','Hide'=>'隐藏','Hide "0.00" value on checkout from referral coupons.'=>'在推荐优惠券的结帐时隐藏“0.00”值。','Hide "Hidden" Products'=>'隐藏 "隐藏 "产品','Hide Add Coupon Form'=>'隐藏添加优惠券表单','Hide commission statistics for non-affiliate coupons.'=>'隐藏非会员优惠券的佣金统计信息。','Hide for logged in users'=>'隐藏登录用户','Hide for logged out users'=>'隐藏已注销用户','Hide for non-affiliate users'=>'隐藏非附属用户','Hide link for non-affiliate users.'=>'隐藏非联盟用户的链接。','Hide on affiliate pages (affiliate dashboard and registration pages)'=>'隐藏联属会员页面（联属会员仪表板和注册页面）','Hide on mobile devices'=>'在移动设备上隐藏','Hide on specific pages'=>'在特定页面上隐藏','Hide on tablet devices'=>'在平板设备上隐藏','Hide Parent Product'=>'隐藏父产品','Hide Settings'=>'隐藏设置','Hide the "all-time" stats on statistics tab and line graph.'=>'将"所有时间"统计数据隐藏在统计选项卡和行图上。','Hide the "Coupon code applied successfully." message on all pages except for the cart/checkout pages.'=>'隐藏"成功应用优惠券代码"，除购物车/结账页面外，所有页面上都显示消息。','Homepage'=>'主页','Hong Kong'=>'香港','Horizontal Margin (X):'=>'水平边距：','How are referral URLs generated?'=>'引荐 URL 是如何生成的？','How did you hear about us?'=>'你是怎么听说我们的？','How do I apply custom tax adjustments to stats and commission?'=>'如何将自定义税务调整应用于统计数据和佣金？','How do I change commission rates for new orders only?'=>'如何仅更改新订单的佣金率？','How do I create affiliate users?'=>'如何创建联盟用户？','How do I get support?'=>'如何获得支持？','How do I give affiliate users access to their own dashboard?'=>'如何让联盟用户访问他们自己的仪表板？','How do I include or exclude tax/VAT from stats and commission?'=>'如何在统计数据和佣金中包含或排除税费/增值税？','How do I manually connect an affiliate to an existing customer as a lifetime affiliate?'=>'如何手动将会员作为终身会员连接到现有客户？','How do I only show “completed” orders on affiliate dashboard?'=>'如何仅在会员仪表板上显示“已完成”的订单？','How do I pay my affiliates?'=>'我如何向我的会员付款？','How long before showing the popup again to the same visitor (0 = show every visit).'=>'向同一访客再次显示弹出窗口的时间（0 = 每次访问都显示）。','How long to wait before showing the popup after page load.'=>'页面加载后等待多长时间才显示弹出窗口。','How many creatives to show per row (on larger screens). Recommended between 2 - 4. On mobile devices this will be responsive, and only shows 1 per row.'=>'每行（在较大的屏幕上）显示多少创意。建议在 2 - 4 之间。在移动设备上，响应响应，并且仅显示每行 1 个。','How many days after being assigned as a "lifetime" referral should it expire, and the customer be unlinked from the customer. Leave empty to use the default global setting. Set to "0" for permanent lifetime commission with no expiry time.'=>'在被分配为“终身”推荐后，该推荐应过期多少天，并且客户应取消与客户的关联。留空以使用默认的全局设置。设置为 “0” 表示永久终身佣金，无到期时间。','How many months to show on the "monthly summary" table by default.'=>'默认情况下，在"月度摘要"表上显示多少个月。','How many of this product would you like to reward the affiliate with?'=>'您想奖励多少该产品？','How much "unpaid commission" must be earned/available, before the affiliate can request a payout.'=>'在关联公司要求付款之前，必须赚取多少未付佣金：','How often should a report be sent to affiliates via email?'=>'报告应多久通过电子邮件发送一次给关联公司？','How often should payout requests be checked & submitted automatically?'=>'应多久检查一次付款请求并自动提交？','How to assign affiliate users to coupons'=>'如何将会员用户分配给优惠券','How to customize the affiliate registration form?'=>'如何自定义会员注册表单？','How to exclude specific products from commission?'=>'如何从佣金中排除特定产品？','How to export affiliate reports in WooCommerce?'=>'如何在WooCommerce中导出会员报告？','How to fix “ERROR: Failed to load ajax request.”'=>'如何修复“错误：无法加载 ajax 请求”。','How To Get Started'=>'如何开始','How to set up encryption:'=>'如何设置加密：','How to set up tiered affiliate commissions?'=>'如何设置分层联盟佣金？','How to track affiliate sales and commissions in WooCommerce?'=>'如何在WooCommerce中跟踪会员销售和佣金？','How to track coupon usage in WooCommerce?'=>'如何在WooCommerce中跟踪优惠券使用情况？','How to use the Coupon Usage Tracker plugin?'=>'如何使用优惠券使用跟踪器插件？','How will you promote us?'=>'你将如何宣传我们？','However, if preferred, you can use a 3rd party wallet plugin for the store credit payouts. This does however require more setup work, and an additional integration plugin.'=>'但是，如果愿意，您可以使用第三方钱包插件进行商店信用额度支付。但是，这确实需要更多的设置工作和额外的集成插件。','https://couponaffiliates.com'=>'https://couponaffiliates.com','https://couponaffiliates.com/'=>'https://couponaffiliates.com/#about','Hungary'=>'匈牙利','I have read and agree to the <a href="%1$s">Affiliate Program Terms of Use</a> and <a href="%2$s">Privacy Policy</a>.'=>'我已阅读并同意<a href="%1$s">会员计划使用条款</a>和<a href="%2$s">隐私政策</a>。','I understand sending without a properly configured SMTP service can cause poor deliverability / spam issues and wish to continue.'=>'我知道在没有正确配置 SMTP 服务的情况下发送邮件会导致送达能力差/垃圾邮件问题，因此希望继续发送。','IBAN'=>'国际银行帐户','IBAN format is invalid. It should be 15-34 characters long.'=>'IBAN 格式无效。长度应为 15-34 个字符。','IBAN format is invalid. Must be valid European IBAN format (provided: \'%s\')'=>'IBAN 格式无效。必须是有效的欧洲 IBAN 格式（提供：\'%s）','IBAN is required for EU bank transfers'=>'欧盟银行转账需要 IBAN','IBAN length is invalid. Must be 15-34 characters (provided: %d characters)'=>'IBAN 长度无效。必须为 15-34 个字符（提供：%d 个字符）','Icon Colour'=>'图标颜色','Icon displayed on the floating button. You can use emojis or text.'=>'浮动按钮上显示的图标。您可以使用表情符号或文本。','Icon Type:'=>'图标类型：','Icons'=>'图标','ID'=>'ID','ID (Newest First)'=>'ID （最新的先显示）','Ideally you should only enable "completed" order statuses above if you have "Completed Date" selected.'=>'理想情况下，只有在您选择了“完成日期”的情况下，您才应该启用上述“已完成”订单状态。','If affiliate statistics need to be recalculated, users will be directed to visit the full dashboard to complete the calculations first.'=>'如果需要重新计算联属会员统计数据，用户将被引导访问完整的仪表板，首先完成计算。','If an order is created using an affiliates coupon, then marked as completed, the commission will be added to the affiliate account as "unpaid commission".'=>'如果使用联盟优惠券创建订单，然后标记为已完成，则佣金将作为“未付佣金”添加到联盟帐户中。','If an order is refunded then the commission will be removed from the users account.'=>'如果订单已退还，则佣金将从用户帐户中删除。','If at-least 1 role is selected, this payout method will only be available for the selected user roles. If none are selected it will be available for all roles.'=>'如果选择了至少 1 个角色，则此收款方式将仅适用于所选用户角色。如果未选择任何内容，则它将可用于所有角色。','If automatic payouts are enabled, this will also trigger the automated payout for Stripe, PayPal and Store Credit.'=>'如果启用了自动提现，这也将触发 Stripe、PayPal 和 Store Credit 的自动提现。','If cookies are disabled, the referral links will still work but will not be as effective, since they can only attempt to auto-apply coupons on the first page they load.'=>'如果禁用 cookie，推荐链接仍然有效，但不会那么有效，因为它们只能尝试在加载的第一个页面上自动应用优惠券。','If disabled, by default the referral will only be tracked if the customer applys the affiliates coupon when placing their order.'=>'如果禁用，默认情况下，仅当客户在下订单时应用会员优惠券时，才会跟踪推荐。','If disabled, it will instead store an extra random ID as a cookie for new referral clicks ("wcusage_referral_id") which will then work in the same way.'=>'如果禁用，它将存储一个额外的随机ID作为cookie，用于新的推荐点击（"wcusage_referral_id"），然后以相同的方式工作。','If disabled, only the first click from the visitor will be tracked (until the cookie expires).'=>'如果禁用，将只跟踪访问者的第一次点击（直到 Cookie 过期）。','If disabled, only the parent (first) order for the subscription will earn commission.'=>'如果禁用，只有父（第一）订单的订阅将赚取佣金。','If disabled, only the parent product will be shown - and variations that have per-variation commission rates set different to the parent.'=>'如果禁用，则仅显示父商品 - 以及按变体佣金率设置为与父商品不同的变体。','If disabled, the parent product will be shown in the table.'=>'如果禁用，父产品将显示在表中。','If disabled, then it will only be able to try to automatically apply the coupon code on their first page visit, and URL only conversion tracking will not work. Coupons will be required to track referrals.'=>'如果禁用，则它只能尝试在他们的第一次页面访问时自动应用优惠券代码，并且仅 URL 转化跟踪将不起作用。需要优惠券来跟踪推荐。','If enabled below, the referral link will automatically apply the coupon code to their cart.'=>'如果在下面启用，推荐链接将自动将优惠券代码应用到他们的购物车。','If enabled, all dashboard links will direct to the portal page, instead of the regular dashboard page.'=>'如果启用，所有仪表板链接都将指向门户页面，而不是常规的仪表板页面。','If enabled, all new referral URL clicks from the same user will be tracked (and increases total clicks + visit logged in click history). Only the latest click will be converted if they make a purchase.'=>'如果启用，将跟踪来自同一用户的所有新转介 URL 单击（并增加总点击次数 + 访问记录在单击历史记录中）。只有最新的点击将转换，如果他们作出购买。','If enabled, all variations of a product will be shown in the table as seperate rows.'=>'如果启用，则产品的所有变体都将在表中显示为单独的行。','If enabled, an option will be displayed in the affiliate dashboard settings tab, allowing affiliates to turn off the email reports.'=>'如果启用，则会在联盟仪表板设置选项卡中显示一个选项，允许关联公司关闭电子邮件报告。','If enabled, if someone visits the site via the referral URL and places an order without using the coupon code, it will still be tracked and award the affiliate.'=>'如果启用，如果有人通过推荐 URL 访问该网站并在不使用优惠券代码的情况下下订单，它仍将被跟踪并奖励会员。','If enabled, only users with one of the selected roles/groups (or the role/group assigned to the selected template) will be auto-accepted.'=>'如果启用，只有具有所选角色/组之一（或分配给所选模板的角色/组）的用户才会被自动接受。','If enabled, order tax will be added to the fixed commission calculations.'=>'如果启用，订单税将添加到固定佣金计算中。','If enabled, order tax will be added to the order subtotal/total/discount for orders in the statistics, and when calculating percentage (%) commission calculations.'=>'如果启用，订单税将添加到统计信息中订单的订单小计/总计/折扣中，并在计算百分比（%）佣金计算时添加。','If enabled, products with their catalog visibility set to "Hidden" will not be shown in the rates table.'=>'如果启用，则目录可见性设置为 "隐藏 "的产品将不会显示在费率表中。','If enabled, store credit will be converted and displayed in the selected currency at checkout. If disabled, all store credit will use the base store currency only.'=>'如果启用，商店积分将在结账时以所选货币进行转换和显示。如果禁用，所有商店积分将只使用基本商店货币。','If enabled, the "MLA Dashboard" will only be accessible to specific affiliate users that you give access to (edit the user and enable "MLA Dashboard Access").'=>'如果启用，“MLA 仪表板”将仅供您授予访问权限的特定关联用户访问（编辑用户并启用“MLA 仪表板访问权限”）。','If enabled, the affiliate reports will be turned on by default for all affiliate users (if they have not yet updated the setting). They can toggle this off in the settings tab of their dashboard. If disabled, then the reports will be turned off by default, and the affiliate user will need to toggle it on to receive the reports.'=>'如果启用，所有联盟用户（如果他们尚未更新设置）默认情况下将打开联盟报告。他们可以在仪表板的设置选项卡中切换此选项卡。如果禁用，则默认情况下将关闭报告，联盟用户需要切换以接收报告。','If enabled, the first time a new dynamic creative is generated for an affiliate, this will be cached for 24 hours, unless the creative is updated. This results better performance and less resource usage.'=>'启用后，首次为联属营销机构生成新的动态广告素材时，系统会缓存 24 小时，除非该广告素材已更新。这样可以提高性能并减少资源使用。','If enabled, the parent product will be hidden from the table if at-least 1 variation.'=>'如果启用，则父商品将在表中隐藏（如果至少有 1 个变体）。','If enabled, the plugin will attempt to apply the code on the first page they visit. If disabled, it will only apply the code once they visit the cart/checkout pages.'=>'如果启用，插件将尝试在第一次访问页面时应用代码。如果禁用，它将仅在购物车/结帐页面上应用代码。','If enabled, the tracking cookies will be deleted from the customers browser, once the order is completed.'=>'如果启用，一旦订单完成，跟踪 cookie 将从客户浏览器中删除。','If enabled, then the registration form shortcode will be disabled/hidden for any affiliate user that is already assigned to an affiliate coupon.'=>'如果启用，则对于已分配到联盟优惠券的任何联盟用户，注册表单将被禁用/隐藏。','If enabled, this tab becomes a link opening in a new browser tab and the header/content settings below are hidden.'=>'如果启用，该标签页将成为在新浏览器标签页中打开的链接，并隐藏下面的页眉/内容设置。','If enabled, when uninstalling (deleting) the plugin, most plugin options and custom tables/data created by this plugin will be deleted. Some data will still remain such as custom order & coupon meta data (if any).'=>'如果启用，当拆装（删除）插件时，将删除此插件创建的大部分插件选项和自定义表/数据。某些数据仍将保留，如自定义订单和优惠券元数据（如果有）。','If enabled, whenever a new user is created (in any way), an affiliate registration will also be submitted for them automatically.'=>'如果启用，每当创建新用户（以任何方式）时，也将自动为他们提交联盟注册。','If enabled, you can select which payout methods should be eligible for automatic payouts.'=>'如果启用，您可以选择哪些支付方式符合自动支付的条件。','If enabled, you can select which payout methods should be used for scheduled payouts.'=>'如果启用，您可以选择应使用哪些收款方式进行预定收款。','If enabled, you can select which payout methods should NOT require or allow invoice uploads.'=>'如果启用，您可以选择哪些付款方式不需要或不允许上传发票。','If for some reason the user deletes/removes the coupon manually from their cart, the cookie will also be removed.'=>'如果出于某种原因，用户从购物车里手动删除优惠券，则 Cookie 也将被删除。','If needed, you can <a href="%s" target="_blank">make the link alone track referrals</a> without requiring the affiliates coupon to be applied, ensuring affiliates receive credit for every sale referred.'=>'如果需要，您可以 <a href="%s">单独使用链接跟踪推荐</a> ，而无需应用会员优惠券，从而确保会员获得推荐的每笔销售的信用。','If no roles are selected, the tab will be visible to all affiliates.'=>'如果未选择任何角色，则该选项卡将对所有关联公司可见。','If none are selected all will have access. This is the user roles that will be able to earn and view this reward.'=>'如果未选择任何内容，则所有人都将具有访问权限。这是将能够获得和查看此奖励的用户角色。','If none are selected, auto-accept will apply to all registrations.'=>'如果没有选择，自动接受将适用于所有注册。','If none selected, all roles will be included.'=>'如果没有选择，则包括所有角色。','If preferred you can disable cookies completely in the'=>'如果愿意，您可以在','If preferred, you can enable "New Customers Only" for individual coupons in the "Usage limits" coupon settings tab.'=>'如果愿意，您可以在"使用限制"优惠券设置选项卡中为单个优惠券启用"仅限新客户"。','If set to "0" then commission will be added to the affiliates account instantly when an order is completed.'=>'如果设置为"0"，则当订单完成时，佣金将立即添加到关联帐户。','If the affiliate does not enter a custom URL, this will be used as the default landing page for the link.'=>'如果联盟成员没有输入自定义 URL，这将用作链接的默认登录页面。','If the affiliate user is assigned to multiple user roles, it will apply the commission rates for the first role it detects with any custom values set.'=>'如果联盟用户被分配到多个用户角色，它将使用设置的任何自定义值对其检测到的第一个角色应用佣金率。','If the affiliates coupon'=>'如果会员优惠券','If the checkbox is selected below, this user has been granted this award/bonus.'=>'如果选中下面的复选框，则此用户已获得此奖励/奖金。','If the referral URL is clicked, the coupon code will automatically be applied to the users checkout. The coupon must be used for commission to be tracked.'=>'如果使用转介 URL，优惠券代码将自动应用于用户结账。优惠券必须用于跟踪佣金。','If the user does not exist, a new one will be created.'=>'如果该用户不存在，则将创建一个新用户。','If the user is an admin, then the ID will also be clickable to open the order page in the backend.'=>'如果用户是管理员，则 ID 也将可单击以打开后端的订单页面。','If the user is not already registered as an affiliate and has no active coupons, this will show the registration from on the affiliate dashboard page.'=>'如果用户尚未注册为 affilaite，并且没有活动优惠券，这将显示从附属仪表板页面上的注册。','If there are no landing pages assigned to the coupon, then this will be hidden.'=>'如果没有分配给优惠券的着陆页，则将隐藏此页面。','If this is disabled, then it will only be able to try to track referrals if they register on their first page visit.'=>'如果禁用此功能，则只有当推荐人在首次访问页面时注册时，它才能尝试跟踪推荐。','If you are experiencing any performance issues or other bugs with the plugin, please try enabling/disabling relevant settings below.'=>'如果您遇到任何性能问题或其他错误与插件，请尝试启用/禁用下面的相关设置。','If you are getting the "Failed to load ajax request" error on the affiliate dashboard'=>'如果您在联盟仪表板上收到“无法加载ajax请求”错误','If you do not want past orders to be affected when commission stats are refreshed, you can enable this in the'=>'如果您不希望在刷新佣金统计数据时影响过去的订单，您可以在','If you dont want the message to always show, toggle this setting on, and it will instead only show on the cart/checkout pages.'=>'如果您不希望邮件始终显示，请切换此设置，而它只会显示在购物车/结账页面上。','If you experience very high volumes of orders for each coupon, this should help greately with affiliate dashboard speed/performance.'=>'如果您体验到每张优惠券的订单量非常大，这应该对附属仪表板的速度/性能有很大的帮助。','If you have any suggestions for new types of bonus requirements or rewards, <a href="%s" target="_blank">please let us know</a>.'=>'如果您对新类型的奖金要求或奖励有任何建议， <a href="%s" target="_blank">请告诉我们</a>。','If you have lots of affiliates, we highly recommend using an SMTP Service Provider via the FluentSMTP plugin for more reliable email delivery.'=>'如果您有很多联属网络营销商，我们强烈建议您通过 FluentSMTP 插件使用 SMTP 服务提供商，以获得更可靠的电子邮件送达。','If you need help getting started, or have any questions at all, you can <a href="%s">create a support ticket</a> any time, and we will be happy to help.'=>'如果您在入门时需要帮助，或者有任何疑问，您可以随时 <a href="%s">创建支持票证</a> ，我们将很乐意为您提供帮助。','If you need to use a different base currency (%s), you will need to upgrade to the "Basic" API plan.'=>'如果您需要使用其他基础货币 （%s），则需要升级到“基本”API 计划。','If you set custom "coupon" commission for that affiliate, or "per product" commission, they WILL take priority over the "user role" commission.'=>'如果您为该联盟会员设置自定义"优惠券"佣金或"每件产品"佣金，他们将优先获得"用户角色"佣金。','If you want conversions to be tracked even if the coupon is not used, enable the setting below under "URL Conversion Tracking".'=>'如果您希望在未使用优惠券的情况下跟踪转化，请在“URL 转化跟踪”下启用以下设置。','If you want to automatically give access to the MLA Dashboard for certain user roles, select them below.'=>'如果您想自动为某些用户角色授予对 MLA 控制面板的访问权限，请在下方选择它们。','If you want to change the text "Coupon" to something else on the checkout page, enable this option and enter the custom text below.'=>'如果您想在结帐页面上将文本“Coupon”更改为其他内容，请启用此选项并在下面输入自定义文本。','If you want to change the word "Affiliate" to something else, enter it here. This will change it everywhere in the plugin except the settings page.'=>'如果您想将 "Affiliate "改成其他词，请在此处输入。这将改变插件中除设置页面以外的所有地方。','If you want to show the logged in users current store credit balance somewhere, use the shortcode'=>'如果要在某个位置显示已登录用户当前的商店信用余额，请使用短代码','If you wish to manually submit payout request for your affiliates, you can do so from this page. After submitting a payout request, you will be redirected to the "Payouts" page to view, manage and finalize the payout.'=>'如果您希望手动为您的关联公司提交付款请求，可以从此页面进行。提交提现请求后，您将被重定向到“提现”页面，以查看、管理和完成提现。','Image'=>'图像','Image:'=>'图像：','Import'=>'进口','Import / Export Custom Tables'=>'导入/导出自定义表','Import and Export the custom database tables created by this plugin.'=>'导入和导出此插件创建的自定义数据库表。','Import Template'=>'导入模板','Import/Export Custom Tables'=>'导入/导出自定义表','Important:'=>'重要：','Important: Affiliate Policy Update'=>'重要：会员政策更新','Important: If your short URLs show a 404 page after changing this, you may need to go to the "Settings > Permalinks" page and click "Save Changes" to refresh your permalinks.'=>'重要提示：如果您的短网址在更改后显示 404 页面，您可能需要转到"永久链接>设置"页面，然后单击"保存更改"以刷新永久链接。','Important: There are some cases where direct link tracking may not be detected properly.'=>'重要提示：在某些情况下，可能无法正确检测到直接链接跟踪。','Important: This is only recommended if you experience high levels of affiliate fraud, and/or want a strict way to help stop unauthorized referrals.'=>'重要提示：仅当您遇到高水平的联盟欺诈和/或希望以严格的方式帮助阻止未经授权的推荐时，才建议这样做。','Important: This needs to be different to your normal affiliate referral URL prefix.'=>'重要提示：这需要与您的普通联盟推荐网址前缀不同。','Important: Wise Bank Transfer payouts do not require the recipient to have a Wise account or email address. The payout is sent directly to their bank account using the provided banking details.'=>'重要提示： 智汇银行转账付款不要求收款人拥有智汇账户或电子邮件地址。付款将使用所提供的银行详细信息直接发送到收款人的银行账户。','in'=>'在','In most cases PayPal Payouts fees are 2%.'=>'在大多数情况下，PayPal支付费用为2%。','In the affiliate report, stats will be shown/calculated based on the previous date range. So monthly reports will show stats from the previous month.'=>'在关联报告中，将根据以前的日期范围显示/计算统计数据。因此，月度报告将显示上月的统计数据。','In this preview, example values are used for the merge tags if the coupon code entered does not exist:'=>'在此预览中，如果输入的优惠券代码不存在，则示例值将用于合并标记：','In this section, you can create your own custom tabs to show on the affiliate dashboard. Shortcode usage supported.'=>'在此部分中，您可以创建自己的自定义选项卡以在附属仪表板上显示。支持短代码使用。','In this section, you can manage multi-currency settings, if you are using a multi currency plugin.'=>'在本节中，如果您使用多货币插件，则可以管理多货币设置。','Include "custom discounts" in % commission calculations & order totals.'=>'在佣金百分比计算和订单总额中包括"自定义折扣"。','Include "fees" in % commission calculations & order totals.'=>'在佣金计算和订单总额中包括"费用"。','Include "shipping costs" in % commission calculations & order totals.'=>'在佣金计算和订单总额百分比中包括"运费"。','Include "taxes" in "fixed" commission calculations.'=>'在"固定"佣金计算中包括"税款"。','Include "taxes" in % commission calculations & order totals.'=>'在佣金计算和订单总额的百分比中包括"税费"。','Include Logo in QR Codes'=>'在 QR 代码中加入徽标','Include the "coupon discount" in % commission calculations.'=>'在佣金百分比计算中包括"优惠券折扣"。','Increase All Future Commission Earned By:'=>'通过以下方式增加所有未来赚取的佣金：','Increase all future commission earnings by percentage'=>'按百分比增加所有未来佣金收入','Increase Commission %'=>'增加佣金 %','Increased'=>'增加','Increased or Decreased'=>'增加或减少','India'=>'印度','Individual Use Only'=>'仅限个人使用','Info'=>'信息','Info & Help'=>'信息与帮助','Information:'=>'信息：','Instead of being a shortcode displayed on a page within your theme, the affiliate portal is its own standalone full-screen page with a modern unique design.'=>'联盟门户不是显示在主题页面上的简码，而是其自己的独立全屏页面，具有现代独特的设计。','Instructions & Plugin Details'=>'说明和插件详细信息','Integrations'=>'集成','International (SWIFT)'=>'国际（SWIFT）','International SWIFT accounts → Receive local currency (converted from your store currency)'=>'国际 SWIFT 账户 → 接收当地货币（从您的商店货币转换而来）','Intro Text'=>'介绍文本','Invalid account email address.'=>'账户电子邮件地址无效。','Invalid account holder name format. Only letters, numbers and basic punctuation allowed.'=>'账户持有人姓名格式无效。只允许使用字母、数字和基本标点符号。','Invalid account number format for this bank type.'=>'该银行类型的账号格式无效。','Invalid address format or missing required address fields.'=>'地址格式无效或缺少必填地址字段。','Invalid affiliate username.'=>'会员用户名无效。','Invalid country code or country not supported by Wise.'=>'国家代码无效或 Wise 不支持的国家。','Invalid coupon code.'=>'优惠券代码无效。','Invalid coupon data.'=>'优惠券数据无效。','Invalid email address.'=>'电子邮件地址无效。','Invalid IBAN format or IBAN not supported for this country.'=>'IBAN 格式无效或该国不支持 IBAN。','Invalid nonce'=>'无效的 nonce','Invalid nonce.'=>'无效 nonce。','Invalid registration data.'=>'注册数据无效。','Invalid request format. Please check all bank details are correctly formatted.'=>'申请格式无效。请检查所有银行信息的格式是否正确。','Invalid request.'=>'无效请求。','Invalid request. Please refresh and try again.'=>'请求无效。请刷新并重试。','Invalid section'=>'无效章节','Invalid SWIFT/BIC code format or bank not found.'=>'SWIFT/BIC 代码格式无效或未找到银行。','Invalid UK sort code format. Must be 6 digits (e.g., 12-34-56).'=>'英国分类代码格式无效。必须为 6 位