显示标记为"已完成"（至少一次）的订单。','Note: If statements are showing "page not found", simply click save in your'=>'注意：如果语句显示"找不到页面"，只需单击保存您的','Note: If you edit this, any previous short URLs created by your affiliates (with the old slug) will stop working.'=>'注意：如果您编辑此内容，则由您的关联公司（使用旧网格）创建的任何之前的短网线都将停止工作。','NOTE: In some rare cases, or certain themes, this option may not work and will show the "loading..." animation continuously. In this case, simply disable it or contact us to look into fixing it for you.'=>'注意：在某些罕见情况下，或某些主题中，此选项可能不起作用，并且将显示"加载..."动画连续。在这种情况下，只需禁用它或联系我们，以研究为您修复它。','Note: Individual product-level rates will take priority over these.'=>'注：个别产品的费率将优先于这些费率。','Note: Payouts can only be made if you have the required funds in your PayPal account.'=>'注意：只有在您的PayPal账户中拥有所需资金时，才能支付款项。','Note: Payouts can only be made if you have the required funds in your Stripe account.'=>'注意：只有当您的 Stripe 账户中有所需资金时，才能进行付款。','Note: There are lots more options available in the settings page.'=>'注意：设置页面中还有更多可用选项。','Note: These will take higher priority than product-level and category-level rates.'=>'注：与产品级和类别级费率相比，这些费率的优先级更高。','Note: This is an integration for a 3rd-party plugin. We are not affiliated with, and do not have any control over the features and functionality offered by the "%s" plugin.'=>'注意：这是第三方插件的集成。我们不隶属于插件，也无法控制“%s”插件提供的特性和功能。','Note: This requires the <a href="%s" target="_blank">multi-currency module</a> to be enabled and configured.'=>'注意：这需要启用和配置 <a href="%s" target="_blank">多币种模块</a>。','Note: This will only show for users that are not currently assigned to any affiliate coupons. They must also be logged in, or have selected "Create an account?" for it to show.'=>'注意：这只会显示给当前未分配到任何联盟优惠券的用户。他们还必须登录，或者已选择"创建帐户？"才能显示。','NOTE: Updating the conversion rates below will only update the totals for NEW orders (if the affiliate dashboard has been viewed at-least once).'=>'注：更新以下转换速率只会更新新订单的总数（如果关联仪表板至少查看过一次）。','Note: We recommended using'=>'注意：我们建议使用','Note: When enabled, any existing orders that do not currently have a conversion rate set, will save the rate as the rate set below (when the affiliate dashboard is next loaded).'=>'注意：启用后，当前没有转换率集的任何现有订单将保存低于下方的费率（当下次加载关联仪表板时）。','Note: When updating these settings saved data will be refreshed for all dashboards automatically (first page load may take longer).'=>'注意：更新这些设置时，所有仪表板的保存数据将自动刷新（第一页加载可能需要更长时间）。','Note: You can customise some other email notifications on the plugin settings page later if needed.'=>'注意：如果需要，您可以稍后在插件设置页面上自定义一些其他电子邮件通知。','Note: You can customise the registration system more in the plugin settings page.'=>'注意：您可以在插件设置页面中更多地自定义注册系统。','Note: Your users can also register themselves as affiliates using the <a href="%s" target="_blank">affiliate registration form</a>.'=>'您的用户还可以使用 <a href="%s" target="_blank">会员注册表</a>将自己注册为会员。','Notes:'=>'备注','Notice (admin only): Page constantly loading? Try refreshing the page.'=>'注意（仅限管理员）：页面不断加载？尝试刷新页面。','Notifications'=>'通知','Notifications Disabled'=>'已禁用通知','Notifications Settings'=>'通知设置','Notify admin when a commission payout is marked as paid.'=>'当佣金支付被标记为已支付时通知管理员。','Notify admin when a new affiliate registration is submitted and awaiting approval.'=>'在提交新的联盟注册并等待批准时通知管理员。','Notify admin when a referred order is cancelled, refunded, or failed.'=>'当推荐的订单被取消、退款或失败时通知管理员。','Notify admin when an affiliate earns commission from a new order.'=>'在联属会员从新订单中赚取佣金时通知管理员。','Notify admin when an affiliate registration is approved.'=>'联盟注册通过后通知管理员。','Notify admin when an affiliate submits a payout request.'=>'在联属会员提交付款请求时通知管理员。','Number of custom tabs'=>'自定义选项卡数量','Number of days the referral cookie is stored'=>'引荐 Cookie 的存储天数','Number of Extra Currencies'=>'额外货币数量','Number of Tiers'=>'层数','On the dashboard, the affiliate can generate their own custom links for specific pages or products on your website.'=>'在仪表板上，联盟成员可以为您网站上的特定页面或产品生成自己的自定义链接。','Once configured, your affiliates can select "Wise Bank Transfer" as their payout method and enter t