sers when their domain is declined for Direct Link Tracking.'=>'当联盟用户的域被拒绝进行直接链接跟踪时，向他们发送电子邮件。','Send an email to affiliate when their affiliate application is accepted.'=>'当其联盟申请被接受时，向联盟发送电子邮件。','Send an email to affiliate when their affiliate application is declined.'=>'当其联盟申请被拒绝时，向联盟发送电子邮件。','Send an email to affiliate when they submit the affiliate application form.'=>'当联盟提交联盟申请表时，向联盟发送电子邮件。','Send an email to affiliates if order they referred has been cancelled, refunded, or failed. Only when status was previously "completed".'=>'如果他们推荐的订单被取消、退款或失败，请向会员发送电子邮件。仅当状态先前为“已完成”时。','Send an email to affiliates when a payout request is successfully marked as paid.'=>'当付款请求被成功标记为已付时，向关联公司发送电子邮件。','Send an email to affiliates whenever their coupon code is used.'=>'每当使用他们的优惠券代码时，向附属公司发送电子邮件。','Send an email to parent affiliate when a new affiliate signs up in their MLA network.'=>'当新的联盟会员在其 MLA 网络中注册时，向父联盟会员发送电子邮件。','Send an email to parent affiliate when a sub-affiliate refers a new order (and it is completed).'=>'当子联盟引用新订单（并且已完成）时，向父联盟成员发送电子邮件。','Send an email to the MLA parent affiliate when a new sub-affiliate registers via their invite link, including the application details and a link to approve or decline from their MLA dashboard.'=>'当有新的次级会员通过其邀请链接注册时，向工作重点母会员发送电子邮件，包括申请详情以及从其工作重点仪表板上批准或拒绝的链接。','Send an email when parent invite enters an email address to send affiliate program invitation.'=>'当家长邀请输入电子邮件地址以发送联盟计划邀请时发送电子邮件。','Send automated SMS text messages to affiliates when key events occur, such as earning new commission or receiving a payout. Powered by Twilio.'=>'在关键事件（如赚取新佣金或收到付款）发生时，向联属会员发送自动短信。由 Twilio 提供支持。','Send automated SMS text messages to affiliates when key events occur.'=>'在关键事件发生时自动向联属会员发送 SMS 短信。','Send Email'=>'发送电子邮件','Send Invite'=>'发送邀请','Send Newsletter'=>'发送通讯','Send Notification Email'=>'发送通知邮件','Send SMS alerts to an admin phone number when key events occur.'=>'关键事件发生时，向管理员电话号码发送短信提醒。','Send Test'=>'发送测试','Send Test SMS'=>'发送测试短信','Send the "Affiliate Application Accepted" email to this affiliate.'=>'向该联盟发送 "联盟申请已接受 "电子邮件。','Send the user an email'=>'向用户发送电子邮件','Send to active affiliates with user role:'=>'发送给具有用户角色的活跃联属会员：','Sending Progress'=>'发送进度','Sending...'=>'发送...','Sensitive bank details are automatically encrypted when you define an encryption key in wp-config.php:'=>'在 wp-config.php 中定义加密密钥后，敏感的银行信息会自动加密：','Sensitive bank details for Wise payouts are being encrypted using your wp-config.php encryption key.'=>'使用 wp-config.php 加密密钥对用于 Wise 付款的敏感银行信息进行加密。','sent'=>'发送','Sent %1$d / %2$d'=>'发送 %1$d / %2$d','Sent to the affiliate when they successfully submit a payout request.'=>'在联属会员成功提交付款申请后发送给他们。','Sent to:'=>'发送至','Sent when a commission payout is marked as paid.'=>'当佣金支付被标记为已支付时发送。','Sent when a referred order is cancelled, refunded, or failed.'=>'推荐订单取消、退款或失败时发送。','Sent when an affiliate earns commission from a new order.'=>'联属会员从新订单中赚取佣金时发送。','Sent when an affiliate registration application is approved by an admin.'=>'当管理员批准联属会员注册申请时发送。','Serif'=>'衬线','Set a custom referrer for orders.'=>'为订单设置自定义引荐来源网址。','Set a different user role for pending affiliate users.'=>'为待决联盟用户设置不同的用户角色。','Set a threshold on the maximum amount that can be paid automatically. Any payout requests above this amount will require manual approval.'=>'设置可自动支付的最高金额的阈值。任何超过此金额的付款请求都需要手动批准。','Set an expiration date for this reward. Leave empty for no expiration date.'=>'设置此奖励的到期日期。留空，无到期日期。','Set custom "flexible commission" amounts for each individual coupon, product, category, or user group/role.'=>'为每个单独的用户角色设置自定义的"灵活佣金"金额。','Set custom commission per affiliate / coupon.'=>'为每个会员/优惠券设置自定义佣金。','Set custom commission per product.'=>'为每个产品设置自定义佣金。','Set custom commission settings for this group.'=>'为此组设置自定义佣金设置。','Set custom MLA commission rates for this specific user. These override both global and group rates. Leave empty to use group or global rates.'=>'为特定用户设置自定义的工作重点佣金率。这将覆盖全局费率和组费率。留空表示使用组或全局费率。','Set custom MLA tier commission rates for this group. These will override the global MLA tier rates for affiliates in this group.'=>'为该组设置自定义 MLA 层级佣金率。这将覆盖该组中联属会员的全局 MLA 层级佣金率。','Set New Commission Rates'=>'设定新的佣金率','Set new commission rates for the affiliate coupon'=>'为联盟优惠券设置新的佣金率','Set the affiliate invite URL variable that will be used in your site URL to identify the referrer and parent affiliate for that user.'=>'设置将在您的网站网址中使用的联盟邀请 URL 变量，以标识该用户的引荐来源网址和父级联属关系。','Set the custom commission rates for each user role below (this is the role of the affiliate user). Leave empty to use default rates.'=>'在下面为每个用户角色设置自定义佣金率（这是联盟用户的角色）。留空以使用默认费率。','Set the primary referral coupon for this order. This will override all other settings, as the default and only coupon that will earn commission from this order.'=>'为此订单设置主要推荐优惠券。这将覆盖所有其他设置，作为默认且唯一将从此订单中赚取佣金的优惠券。','Set the referral URL variable that will be used in your site URL to identify the referrer and to automatically apply that coupon, and track clicks.'=>'设置将在您的网站 URL 中使用的转介 URL 变量，以识别推荐人并自动应用该优惠券并跟踪点击。','Set the referral URL variable that will be used to identify the campaign.'=>'设置用于识别活动的转介 URL 变量。','Set to "0" for permanent lifetime commission with no expiry time.'=>'设置为"0"永久终身佣金，没有到期时间。','Set Your Commission Rates'=>'设置佣金费率','SETTINGS'=>'设置','Settings'=>'设置','Settings & Customization'=>'设置和定制','Settings not saving correctly? Switch saving mode'=>'设置保存不正确？切换保存模式','Settings not saving? Try disabling "legacy" saving, or increasing your PHP "max_input_vars" in your hosting configuration to 1000 or higher (currently %s).'=>'设置未保存？尝试禁用 “legacy” 保存，或将主机配置中的 PHP “max_input_vars” 增加到 1000 或更高（当前为 %s）。','settings page'=>'设置页面','Settings Saved'=>'已保存的设置','Settings updated successfully.'=>'设置已成功更新。','Setup'=>'设置','Setup a CAPTCHA on your affiliate registration form to help prevent spam.'=>'在您的联盟注册表上设置 Google 重新捕获，以帮助防止垃圾邮件。','Setup Checklist'=>'设置清单','Setup Guide'=>'设置指南','Setup Guide – How to get started!'=>'设置指南 – 如何开始！','Setup Instruction