用 {company} 插入关联公司名称。','Use {coupon} to insert the coupon code.'=>'使用 {优惠券} 插入优惠券代码。','Use {discount} to insert the coupon discount percentage or fixed amount.'=>'使用 {discount} 插入优惠券折扣百分比或固定金额。','Use {first-name} to insert the affiliate first name.'=>'使用 {名字} 插入关联公司的名字。','Use {qrcode} to insert the a QR code of the affiliate default referral URL.'=>'使用 {qrcode} 插入会员默认推荐 URL 的二维码。','Use {username} to insert the affiliate username.'=>'使用 {用户名} 插入关联用户名。','Used when describing the store credit payment/transaction in the logs.'=>'在日志中描述商店信用付款/交易时使用。','Useful if you simply want a generic "affiliate" page to direct affiliates to, instead of a unique link for each one.'=>'如果您只是想要一个通用的"联盟"页面来引导联营公司，而不是每个"附属"页面的独特链接，则非常有用。','User'=>'用户','User ID'=>'用户 ID','User not found.'=>'未找到用户。','User Registration'=>'用户注册','User Restrictions'=>'用户限制','User Role'=>'用户角色：','User role required for plugin admin capabilities:'=>'插件管理功能所需的权限：','User role:'=>'用户角色：','User Roles:'=>'用户角色：','User updated successfully.'=>'用户更新成功。','User:'=>'用户：','Username'=>'用户名','Username...'=>'用户名...','Usernames cannot be changed.'=>'用户名不可更改。','Users'=>'用户','Users combined total commission from referral link and their MLA sub-affiliates.'=>'用户将推荐链接及其MLA子附属公司的总佣金合并在一起。','Using One License for Live & Staging Sites'=>'对实时和暂存站点使用一个许可证','Vertical Margin (Y):'=>'垂直边距：','via'=>'通过','View'=>'查看','View "Creatives" Settings'=>'查看"广告素材"设置','View "Direct Link Tracking" Settings'=>'查看"直接链接跟踪"设置','View "Referral Popup" Settings'=>'查看 "推荐弹出窗口 "设置','View %s'=>'查看 %s','View %s Dashboard'=>'查看 %s 控制面板','View %s dashboard'=>'查看 %s 仪表板','View a log of all the activity that has taken place in your affiliate program.'=>'查看您的联盟计划中发生的所有活动的日志。','View Affiliate'=>'查看联属公司','View Affiliate Dashboard'=>'查看联盟仪表板','View affiliate dashboard'=>'查看联盟仪表板','View All'=>'查看全部','View All Documentation'=>'查看所有文档','View all visits for this campaign name.'=>'查看此广告系列名称的所有访问。','View all visits for this coupon.'=>'查看此优惠券的所有访问。','View all visits for this referrer.'=>'查看此推荐人的所有访问。','View and manage all of your affiliate coupons, and access links to each of their affiliate dashboards on the <a href="%s" target="_blank">coupons list</a> page.'=>'在 <a href="%s" target="_blank">优惠券列表</a>页面上查看和管理所有联属优惠券，并访问每个联属会员仪表板的链接。','View Bonus'=>'查看奖金','VIEW BONUSES'=>'查看奖金','View Bonuses'=>'查看奖金','View Changelog'=>'查看更新日志','View Coupons List & Unique Links'=>'查看优惠券列表和唯一链接','VIEW CREATIVES'=>'查看广告素材','View Creatives'=>'查看广告素材','View Dashboard'=>'查看仪表板','View Documentation'=>'查看文档','View Full Activity Log'=>'查看完整活动日志','View Full Dashboard'=>'查看完整仪表盘','View Full Report'=>'查看完整报告','View in PayPal'=>'在PayPal查看','View in Stripe'=>'在条纹中查看','View Landing Page'=>'查看着陆页面','View MLA Affiliate'=>'查看工作重点附属机构','View MLA dashboard'=>'查看工作重点仪表板','View MLA Details'=>'查看工作重点详情','View More'=>'查看更多','VIEW NEWSLETTERS'=>'查看时事通讯','View Order in Backend (Admin Only)'=>'在后端查看订单（仅限管理员）','View Page'=>'查看页面','View payouts setup guide'=>'查看支付设置指南','View Product'=>'查看产品','View Reports'=>'查看报告','View setup guide'=>'查看设置指南','View Short URL'=>'查看短网址','View the affiliate dashboard for this affiliate coupon.'=>'查看此联盟优惠券的联盟仪表板。','View the latest updates and changelog on our website:'=>'在我们的网站上查看最新更新和变更日志：','View transaction in PayPal.'=>'以PayPal查看交易。','View transaction in Stripe.'=>'查看条纹交易。','View User'=>'查看用户','Viewing as'=>'查看方式','Viewing as:'=>'查看为：','Viewing MLA dashboard for user:'=>'查看用户的 MLA 仪表板：','Visibility'=>'可见性','Visibility Settings'=>'可见性设置','Visible'=>'可见','Visit Date'=>'访问日期','Visit deleted successfully.'=>'访问已成功删除。','Visit Full Dashboard'=>'访问完整仪表板','Visit the <a href="%s" target="_blank">settings page</a> to edit more options, enable more features, and customise your affiliate program to work exactly how you want!'=>'访问 <a href="%s">设置页面</a> 以编辑更多选项，并自定义您的联盟计划以完全按照您想要的方式工作！','Visitor ID'=>'访客编号','Visitors Blacklist'=>'访客黑名单','Visitors referred directly from any of these domains will not have referrals tracked or coupons applied automatically.'=>'直接从任何这些域推荐的访问者将不会跟踪推荐或自动应用优惠券。','Visits'=>'参观','Waiting for recipient information'=>'等待收件人信息','Waiting for you to fund this transfer'=>'等待您为这次转账提供资金','Wallet System'=>'钱包系统','Want more advanced coupon usage restrictions? Check out our %s plugin!'=>'想要更高级的优惠券使用限制？看看我们的 %s 插件吧！','Want more advanced coupon usage restrictions? Check out the %s plugin.'=>'想要更高级的优惠券使用限制？查看 %s 插件。','Want more advanced features?'=>'想要更多高级功能？','Want us to create a new plugin integration?'=>'希望我们创建一个新的插件集成？','Warning:'=>'警告','Warning: By default this may effect all previous calculations and statistics if the system were to "refresh data" at any point. You can prevent previous commission from being affected, <a href="%s" target="_blank" style="color: red;">click here for details</a>.'=>'警告：默认情况下，如果系统在任何时候 "刷新数据"，这可能会影响以前的所有计算和统计。您可以通过<a href="%s" target="_blank" style="color:红色;">单击此处了解详情</a>，防止以前的委托受到影响。','Warning: Cloudflare Automatic Platform Optimization (APO) appears to be enabled. This may cause issues with referral cookies and coupon auto-apply features.'=>'警告：Cloudflare 自动平台优化 (APO) 似乎已启用。这可能会导致推荐 cookie 和优惠券自动应用功能出现问题。','Warning: If you use this option, you should be even more careful of fraudulent activity. We do recommend reviewing and accepting payouts manually instead, simply so you can make sure each payout is valid and non-fraudulent.'=>'警告：如果使用此选项，则应更加小心欺诈活动。我们建议您改为手动查看和接受付款，这样您就可以确保每次付款都是有效且非欺诈性的。','Warning: LiteSpeed web server detected. Cookie stripping may be enabled, which can cause issues with referral cookies and coupon auto-apply features.'=>'警告：检测到 LiteSpeed 网络服务器。Cookie 剥离可能已启用，这会导致推荐 Cookie 和优惠券自动应用功能出现问题。','Warning: You have "<a href="%s" target="_blank">Anyone can register</a>" disabled in WordPress, which will be ignored for the registration form on the affiliate dashboard.'=>'警告：您在 WordPress 中禁用了"<a href="%s" target="_blank">任何人都可以注册</a>"，联盟仪表板上的注册表单将忽略这一点。','Warning: You have "<a href="%s" target="_blank">Anyone can register</a>" disabled in WordPress, which will be ignored for the registration form on the affiliate portal.'=>'警告：您在 WordPress 中禁用了"<a href="%s" target="_blank">任何人都可以注册</a>"，联盟门户网站上的注册表单将忽略这一点。','Warning: You will want to create a "template coupon" and assign it in the settings for affiliate coupons to be generated properly.'=>'警告：您将需要创建一个“模板优惠券”，并在设置中分配它，以便正确生成联盟优惠券。','was updated'=>'已更新','We are going to run you through some of the most important settings in the Coupon Affiliates plugin, to help you get everything setup!'=>'我们将引导您完成优惠券联盟插件中一些最重要的设置，以帮助您完成一切设置！','We are reviewing your application and will be in touch soon!'=>'我们正在审核您的申请，并会尽快与您联系！','We highly recommend that you keep this option DISABLED, as it may cause some issues, or paying too much commission.'=>'我们强烈建议您将此选项保留为禁用状态，因为它可能会导致一些问题或支付过多的佣金。','We Increased Your Commission Rate'=>'我们提高了您的佣金率','We Miss You – Let’s Get You Earning Again'=>'我们想念你--让我们一起为你赚钱吧','Website'=>'网站','Website:'=>'网站：','Weekly'=>'周刊','Welcome & Program Update'=>'欢迎辞和计划更新','Welcome to Our Affiliate Program + Quick Update'=>'欢迎加入我们的联属会员计划 + 快速更新','Welcome to the Coupon Affiliates setup wizard!'=>'欢迎来到优惠券联盟设置向导！','What happens when an order is refunded or partially refunded?'=>'订单退款或部分退款时会发生什么？','What is a "coupon-based" affiliate program?'=>'什么是“基于优惠券”的联盟计划？','What is your preferred affiliate coupon code?'=>'您首选的联盟优惠券代码是什么？','What should happen after form submission?'=>'提交表格后会发生什么？','What time of the day should payouts be requested automatically?'=>'应自动要求在一天中的什么时间付款？','What time of the day should reports be sent?'=>'应在一天中的什么时间发送报告？','What toggles should be shown for statistics and line graphs?'=>'应为统计数据和折线图显示哪些切换？','What type of coupon would you like?'=>'您想要什么类型的优惠券？','WhatsApp Text'=>'WhatsApp Text','When a payout request is submitted, you will be able to view, manage, and pay it from the admin "<a href="%s">Payouts</a>" page.'=>'提交收款请求后，您将能够从管理员的“<a href="%s">收款</a>”页面查看、管理和付款。','When a referral coupon is applied, if the discount is "0.00", it will hide the 0.00 discount line on the checkout page.'=>'使用推荐优惠券时，如果折扣为“0.00”，则会在结帐页面上隐藏 0.00 折扣行。','When a user submits the form, you will be notified, and can review the application in the admin "Registrations" page.'=>'当用户提交表单时，您将收到通知，并可以在管理员的“注册”页面中查看应用程序。','When an affiliate adds a new domain to their account, an email will be sent to your admin email, with a link to approve or deny the domain.'=>'当联盟会员将新域添加到其帐户时，系统会向您的管理员电子邮件发送一封电子邮件，其中包含用于批准或拒绝该域的链接。','When approved, it will generate a coupon code automatically, and assign it to that affiliate user.'=>'获得批准后，它将自动生成优惠券代码，并将其分配给该联盟用户。','When assigning users to coupons, if this is enabled, it will only show the list of users with the custom "coupon affiliate" role.'=>'将用户分配到优惠券时，如果启用此优惠券，则仅显示具有自定义"优惠券联盟"角色的用户列表。','When checked, this coupon can only be used by new customers on their first order.'=>'选中后，此优惠券只能由新客户在第一个订单上使用。','When completing this form, it will automatically submit an approved %s registration for that user, automatically creating the coupon and assigning them to it.'=>'填写此表单后，它将自动为该用户提交会员注册，自动创建优惠券并将其分配给它。','When disabled, if there are no users assigned to a coupon, the dashboard can be viewed by anyone if they visit the unique URL directly. However, if there is a user assigned to it, the URL will be private.'=>'禁用后，如果没有用户分配到优惠券，则任何人都可以直接访问唯一 URL，从而查看仪表板。但是，如果为其分配了用户，则该 URL 将是私有的。','When disabled, if you change commission rates, it will automatically update the stats/commission for ALL new and past orders on the affiliate dashboard.'=>'禁用后，如果您更改佣金率，它将自动更新联盟仪表板上所有新订单和过去订单的统计数据/佣金。','When disabled, it will only allow 1 affiliate coupon to be used per order. (This is any coupons that have an affiliate user assigned to them.)'=>'禁用后，每次订单只能使用 1 个附属优惠券。（这是任何将附属用户分配给他们的优惠券。','When disabled, the affiliate user will be prevented from using their own coupon code (coupons they are assigned to) at cart or checkout.'=>'禁用后，联营用户将被禁止在购物车或结账时使用自己的优惠券代码（他们被分配到的优惠券）。','When enabled, "Processing Commission" will be tracked and shown on the payouts tab for statuses that are set to show on the dashboard but not completed yet (not granted unpaid commission).'=>'启用后，"处理佣金 "将被跟踪，并显示在已设置为在仪表板上显示但尚未完成（未支付佣金）的状态的支付选项卡上。','When enabled, % commission will be calculated based on the order subtotal/total including "fees". It will also be added to the subtotal/total shown in statistics.'=>'启用后，佣金百分比将根据订单小计/总计（包括"费用"）计算。它还将添加到统计信息中显示的小计/总计中。','When enabled, % commission will be calculated based on the order subtotal/total including "shipping costs".'=>'启用后，佣金百分比将根据订单小计/总计（包括“运费”）计算。','When enabled, % commission will be calculated before any custom discounts are deducted from the subtotal/total. It will also be added to the subtotal/total shown in statistics.'=>'启用后，将在从小计/总计中扣除任何自定义折扣之前计算佣金百分比。它还将添加到统计信息中显示的小计/总计中。','When enabled, % commission will be calculated on the order subtotal (instead of total), before the coupon discount is deducted from it.'=>'启用后，佣金百分比将在订单小计（而不是总计）上计算，然后从中扣除优惠券折扣。','When enabled, a "MLA Dashboard" link will be shown on the normal coupon affiliate dashboard, at the top right, next to the "Logout" link.'=>'启用后，“MLA仪表板”链接将显示在普通优惠券联盟仪表板上，位于右上角的“注销”链接旁边。','When enabled, a "statement" PDF file will be generated automatically whenever payout requests are made by the affiliate. These statements show the payout details, status, company information, etc.'=>'启用后，每当关联公司提出付款请求时，将自动生成"声明"PDF 文件。这些报表显示付款详情、状态、公司信息等。','When enabled, a new "Payout Statement Details" section is displayed in the "Settings" tab of the affiliate dashboard, to enter their billing data to show on statements.'=>'启用后，新的"付款声明详细信息"部分将显示在关联仪表板的"设置"选项卡中，以输入其计费数据以显示在报表上。','When enabled, a new checkbox will appear on store checkout, under order notes, for them to join the affiliate program. This will submit an affiliate registration application for the user.'=>'启用后，商店结账时将在订单备注下显示一个新复选框，供他们加入联盟计划。这将为用户提交联盟注册申请。','When enabled, a phone number field will appear on the affiliate registration form. The submitted number is saved as the affiliate\'s phone and used for SMS notifications.'=>'启用后，联属会员注册表上将显示电话号码字段。提交的电话号码将被保存为联属会员的电话，并用于短信通知。','When enabled, affiliate coupons can only be applied if the customer currently has the tracking cookie from that affiliate referral link.'=>'启用后，只有当客户当前拥有来自联属推荐链接的跟踪 cookie 时，才能应用联属优惠券。','When enabled, affiliates can download a statement for both pending and completed payouts. If disabled, they can only download statements for completed payouts.'=>'启用后，关联公司可以下载待决和已完成付款的报表。如果禁用，他们只能下载已完成付款的报表。','When enabled, affiliates can enter their phone number in the dashboard to receive SMS notifications. If they leave it blank, no SMS will be sent to them.'=>'启用后，联属会员可在仪表板中输入电话号码，以接收短信通知。如果留空，则不会向他们发送短信。','When enabled, ALL the parent affiliates calculated commissions (from every tier) will be deducted from the main sub-affiliates earned commission amount for each order.'=>'启用后，所有母级联盟计算的佣金（来自每个等级）将从主要子联盟成员为每个订单赚取的佣金金额中扣除。','When enabled, all unique affiliate dashboard URLs will ALWAYS be private, and only be visible to the assigned user (and admins).'=>'启用后，所有唯一的联盟仪表板 URL 将始终是私有的，并且仅对分配的用户（和管理员）可见。','When enabled, an opt-out checkbox will appear on the affiliate dashboard settings tab.'=>'启用后，联属会员仪表板设置选项卡上将出现退出复选框。','When enabled, commission statistics are disabled/hidden for coupons that are not assigned to an affiliate user.'=>'启用后，将禁用/隐藏未分配给联盟用户的优惠券的佣金统计信息。','When enabled, commission will be calculated and displayed on the affiliate dashboard.'=>'启用后，佣金将被计算并显示在会员仪表板上。','When enabled, dark mode styling will be available for the affiliate dashboard.'=>'启用后，联属会员仪表板将采用暗色模式样式。','When enabled, dark mode will be the default theme. Users can still toggle to light mode if the toggle is enabled.'=>'启用后，深色模式将成为默认主题。如果启用了切换功能，用户仍可切换到浅色模式。','When enabled, if a customer uses an MLA users affiliate coupon code in an order, that customer will also automatically be assigned as a sub-affiliate in their MLA network (if not already assigned to one).'=>'启用后，如果客户在订单中使用 MLA 用户关联优惠券代码，则该客户也将自动分配为其 MLA 网络中的子代理（如果尚未分配给子代理）。','When enabled, if a new affiliate registers via an MLA invite link, the MLA parent will be notified and will be able to approve or decline the registration from the "Invite" tab of their MLA dashboard. The registration will still require final approval from a site admin if the main registrations approval flow requires it.'=>'启用后，如果有新的联属会员通过 MLA 邀请链接注册，MLA 家长将收到通知，并可在其 MLA 面板的 "邀请 "选项卡上批准或拒绝注册。如果主注册审批流程需要，注册仍需要网站管理员的最终批准。','When enabled, if an MLA invite link is visited, the link will also work like a normal affiliate referral link, to apply the coupon to cart and track affiliate referrals if they place an order.'=>'启用后，如果访问了MLA邀请链接，则该链接也将像普通的会员推荐链接一样工作，以将优惠券应用于购物车并在会员推荐下订单时跟踪他们。','When enabled, the "Request Payout" button will be shown on the affiliate dashboard, allowing affiliates to manually request payouts.'=>'启用后，“请求付款”按钮将显示在联盟管理平台上，允许联盟成员手动请求付款。','When enabled, the affiliate can enter a custom amount for their payout request. The minimum amount will still be the payment threshold, and maximum amount is their total available unpaid commission.'=>'启用后，联盟成员可以为其付款请求输入自定义金额。最低金额仍将是付款阈值，最大金额是他们可用的未付佣金总额。','When enabled, the affiliate will be required to enter their payment details before they can request a payout.'=>'启用后，联盟会员将被要求输入其付款详细信息，然后才能请求付款。','When enabled, the checkbox to join the affiliate program will be checked automatically.'=>'启用后，将自动选中加入联盟计划的复选框。','When enabled, the PAST orders will not be affected (even if clicking "refresh data"), and it will only set the updated rates for NEW orders. The only time it WILL be updated is if an order is refunded.'=>'启用后，PAST订单将不受影响（即使单击“刷新数据”），并且只会为新订单设置更新的费率。它唯一会更新的时间是订单退款。','When enabled, the rates below will override group and global rates.'=>'启用后，以下费率将覆盖组和全局费率。','When enabled, the unpaid commission will also not be added to non-affiliate coupons.'=>'启用后，未付的佣金也不会添加到非联盟优惠券中。','When enabled, this will also show the adjusted "total" and "subtotal" (with deducted percentage) on affiliate dashboard. When disabled, only the "commission" stat will be affected by the adjustment.'=>'启用后，这还将在联属仪表板上显示调整后的"总"和"子整体"（扣除百分比）。当禁用时，只有"佣金"统计将受调整的影响。','When enabled, visitors referred by blocked domains will be completely blocked from entering any affiliate coupons manually (as long as the cookie is saved).'=>'启用后，被阻止域引用的访问者将被完全阻止手动输入任何联盟优惠券（只要保存cookie）。','When enabled, you can override the global MLA tier rates on a per-group basis (via Affiliate Groups > Edit Group) or per-user basis (via the WordPress user profile or admin affiliate page).'=>'启用后，您可以按组（通过联属会员组 > 编辑组）或按用户（通过 WordPress 用户配置文件或管理联属会员页面）覆盖全局工作重点层级费率。','When selected, a "Status" dropdown will be shown as an option when filtering by date range. Will only show if you have more than 1 status enabled.'=>'选中后，按日期范围过滤时，“状态”下拉菜单将显示为一个选项。仅当您启用了 1 个以上的状态时才会显示。','When selected, below the orders table it will show the total number of orders for each status. The "Status" column needs to be enabled.'=>'选择后，在订单表下方，它将显示每种状态的订单总数。需要启用“状态”列。','When selected, the totals for all orders within the selected date range will be shown in a new row at the bottom of the recent orders and monthly summary table.'=>'选中后，所选日期范围内所有订单的总计将显示在最近订单和每月汇总表底部的新行中。','When someone uses the referral URL, if the code is automatically applied, it will show this message on all pages.'=>'当某人使用转介 URL 时，如果自动应用代码，它将在所有页面上显示此消息。','When they submit the affiliate registration form you can then view and edit the coupon code they have entered, before approving the affiliate registration.'=>'当他们提交联盟注册表格时，您可以在批准联盟注册之前查看和编辑他们输入的优惠券代码。','When updating these settings, you may need to click the "REFRESH ALL DATA" button in the "Debug" tab for changes to show immediately for existing orders.'=>'更新这些设置时，您可能需要单击"调试"选项卡中的"刷新所有数据"按钮，以便立即为现有订单显示更改。','When you accept an affiliate, a new coupon is created with the same settings, and is automatically assigned to user.'=>'当您接受联盟会员时，将使用相同的设置创建新的优惠券，并自动分配给用户。','When you create an affiliate user, or accept an affiliate registration, their coupon code is automatically created and assigned to them. They will automatically be sent an email which includes a link to their dashboard. You can customize this email in the plugin settings.'=>'当您创建联盟用户或接受联盟注册时，他们的优惠券代码会自动创建并分配给他们。他们将自动收到一封电子邮件，其中包含指向其仪表板的链接。您可以在插件设置中自定义此电子邮件。','When you process a payout, the plugin will create a transfer in your Wise account using the provided bank details. You will then need to verify and complete the transfer in Wise.'=>'当您处理付款时，插件将使用所提供的银行详细信息在您的 Wise 账户中创建转账。然后，您需要在 Wise 中验证并完成转账。','Where can I get plugin support?'=>'我在哪里可以获得插件支持？','where product ID is'=>'其中产品 ID 为','Where to redirect when clicking the button. Leave empty to use shop page.'=>'点击按钮时的重定向位置。留空以使用商店页面。','Where to redirect when clicking the button. Leave empty to use shop page. The coupon will be auto-applied.'=>'点击按钮时的重定向位置。留空以使用商店页面。优惠券将自动应用。','Which custom commission values should be applied as priority?'=>'应优先应用哪些自定义佣金值？','Who can apply affiliate coupons to their cart?'=>'谁可以将联盟优惠券应用到他们的购物车？','Widget Colors'=>'小工具颜色','Widget not available for this page/user.'=>'此页面/用户无法使用小工具。','Widget Position:'=>'小部件位置：','Wise'=>'明智','Wise API did not return a recipient ID. Response: '=>'Wise API 未返回收件人 ID。响应：','Wise API error: '=>'Wise API 错误：','Wise Bank Transfer'=>'明智银行转账','Wise Bank Transfer Payouts'=>'明智的银行转账付款','Wise Bank Transfer payouts allow you to pay affiliates directly to their bank accounts using Wise\'s low-cost international transfer service.'=>'慧科银行转帐付款允许您使用慧科的低成本国际转帐服务直接向联属会员的银行帐户付款。','Wise Bank Transfer Payouts allows you to one-click pay your affiliates directly to their bank account through Wise with low transfer fees.'=>'Wise 银行转账付款允许您通过 Wise 以较低的转账费用一键式直接向联属会员的银行账户付款。','Wise cancellation function not available. Transfer ID: '=>'不提供明智取消功能。转账 ID：','Wise fees vary based on the currency and destination.'=>'手续费因货币和目的地而异。','Wise Payouts'=>'明智支付','Wise Status:'=>'明智状态：','With admin reports, you can view statistics and analytics for all your coupons and affiliates.'=>'通过管理员报告，您可以查看所有优惠券和附属公司的统计数据和分析。','With lifetime commission enabled, once someone uses the affiliates coupon code, that customer will be linked to the affiliate forever, and ALL future purchases from that customer and will count as a referral, even if they dont re-use the coupon code.'=>'启用终身佣金后，一旦有人使用联营优惠券代码，该客户将永久链接到关联公司，并且将来从该客户处购买的所有产品都将计入转介，即使他们不再重复使用优惠券代码。','With the "[couponaffiliates]" shortcode, when a user visits this page (without the unique URL ID), enable to show full affiliate dashboard automatically if the affiliate user is only assigned to one coupon.'=>'使用"[优惠券附属]"短代码，当用户访问此页面（没有唯一的 URL ID）时，如果关联用户只被分配到一个优惠券，则能够自动显示完整的联盟仪表板。','With the free version, you will need to manually handle payouts and payment details. There are a few ways that you can do this, such as generating a detailed admin report. <a href="%s">Click here to learn more.</a>'=>'使用免费版本，您将需要手动处理付款和付款详细信息。有几种方法可以做到这一点，例如生成详细的管理报告。 <a href="%s">点击这里了解更多。</a>','With the Multi-Level Affiliates module, your existing affiliates can invite new users to register as an affiliate on your website.'=>'使用 Multi-Level Affiliates 模块，您现有的 Affiliates 可以邀请新用户在您的网站上注册为联盟。','With the PRO version can also set commission rates per each individual affiliate/coupon, or product.'=>'使用PRO版本还可以为每个单独的联盟/优惠券或产品设置佣金率。在下面了解更多信息。','With the Pro version get access to unlimited date range on the admin reports, export to CSV, and access to date comparison features, to compare analytics between 2 sets of dates'=>'随着 Pro 版本在管理员报告中访问无限日期范围，导出到 CSV，并访问日期比较功能，以比较 2 套日期之间的分析','with the settings you want the gift coupons to include, and enter the name here. The new gift coupons generated will copy all the settings from this template.'=>'使用您希望包含礼券的设置，然后在此处输入名称。生成的新礼品券将复制此模板中的所有设置。','With this disabled, only logged in users can apply.'=>'使用此禁用时，只能登录用户进行申请。','With this enabled commission will be paid instantly into the affiliate account automatically, as soon as they request a payout. This will apply to Stripe, PayPal and Store Credit payout methods.'=>'启用此佣金后，一旦他们请求付款，佣金将立即自动支付到联盟帐户中。这将适用于 Stripe、PayPal 和 Store Credit 付款方式。','With this enabled, "administrator" users will be able to fill out the affiliate registration form for new users (custom username/email etc), whilst logged in.'=>'启用此功能后，"管理员"用户将能够在登录时填写新用户的联盟注册表（自定义用户名/电子邮件等）。','With this enabled, a hidden field will be added to the registration form to help prevent spam.'=>'启用此功能后，将向注册表单中添加一个隐藏字段，以帮助防止垃圾邮件。','With this enabled, a new "Affiliate" link will appear on the users "My Account" page menu. This will take them to the affiliate dashboard page selected above.'=>'启用此功能后，用户"我的帐户"页面菜单上将显示新的"联盟"链接。这将带他们到上面选择的联盟仪表板页面。','With this enabled, a new "Upload Invoice" option will be displayed above the "Request Payout" button on the "Payouts" tab. They can click this to upload their PDF invoice for the payout, then submit their payout request.'=>'启用此功能后，新的"上传发票"选项将显示在"付款"选项卡上的"请求付款"按钮上方。他们可以单击此操作以上传付款的 PDF 发票，然后提交付款请求。','With this enabled, a second password field will be shown to require users to confirm their password.'=>'启用此功能后，将显示第二个密码字段，要求用户确认其密码。','With this enabled, admin accounts will also be able to view the "payouts" tab when viewing any of the affiliate coupon dashboard pages.'=>'启用此功能后，管理员帐户在查看任何联盟优惠券页面时还可以查看"付款"选项卡。','With this enabled, affiliate registrations will be automatically accepted (and coupon auto-created instantly), instead of manual approval.'=>'启用此功能后，将自动接受关联注册（并立即自动创建优惠券），而不是手动批准。','With this enabled, affiliate users can click a button to automatically generate a short URL for their referral link.'=>'启用此功能后，联盟用户可以单击按钮，自动生成其转介链接的短网址。','With this enabled, affiliate users can click a button to generate a QR code for their referral link.'=>'启用此功能后，联盟用户可以单击按钮以生成其转介链接的 QR 代码。','With this enabled, affiliate users can link their website domain to their coupon.'=>'启用此功能后，联盟用户可以将其网站域链接到其优惠券。','With this enabled, all renewals for subscriptions will also be rewarded commission (if the affiliate referred the customer) and renewal orders displayed on the dashboard.'=>'启用此功能后，订阅的所有续订也将获得奖励佣金（如果关联公司转介客户）和仪表板上显示的续订订单。','With this enabled, if someone follows a referral link and registers (creates an account), they will then be linked to that affiliate, even without initially placing an order.'=>'启用此功能后，如果有人点击推荐链接并注册（创建帐户），即使最初没有下订单，他们也会被链接到该联盟会员。','With this enabled, in the "referral URL" section your affiliates will be able to create "campaigns", to generate custom URLs, track clicks, sales, conversation rate for specific referral campaigns.'=>'启用此功能后，在"推荐 URL"部分，您的关联公司将能够创建"活动"，生成自定义网址、跟踪点击率、销售、特定推荐活动的对话率。','With this enabled, instead of the user entering their "preferred coupon code", a code will be generated for them automatically.'=>'启用此功能后，用户将自动为他们生成格式化代码，而不是用户输入其"首选优惠券代码"。','With this enabled, instead of using the default WordPress "subscriber" user role, new affiliate users will be assigned to the custom "coupon affiliate" user role (or the custom role defined below) instead.'=>'启用此功能后，新联盟用户将改用自定义的"优惠券联盟"用户角色（或下面定义的自定义角色），而不是使用默认 WordPress"订阅者"用户角色。','With this enabled, it will permanently save and use the conversion rate that was set at the time the order is created, even if you update the rates below.'=>'启用此功能后，即使您更新了下面的费率，它也会永久保存并使用订单创建时设置的佣金率。','With this enabled, logged out users can view the registration form (with some extra fields). When submitted it will create a new account for them, and submit the affiliate application.'=>'启用此功能后，注销的用户可以查看注册表（带有一些额外的字段）。提交后，它将为他们创建一个新帐户，并提交联盟申请。','With this enabled, multiple template coupons will be available and the affiliate will be able to choose which type they want via the registration form.'=>'启用此功能后，将提供多个模板优惠券，并且联盟会员将能够通过注册表选择他们想要的类型。','With this enabled, some of the fields on the form will be displayed in 2 columns, such as first and last name.'=>'启用此功能后，表单上的某些字段将显示在 2 列中，例如名字和姓氏。','With this enabled, the affiliate can only request a payout if they have attached an invoice (PDF file).'=>'启用此功能后，关联公司只能在已附加发票 （PDF 文件） 的情况下请求付款。','With this enabled, the first ever payout request by an affiliate will require manual approval. After they have at-least 1 completed payout, all future payouts can be paid automatically.'=>'启用此功能后，联盟会员的首次付款请求将需要手动批准。在他们至少完成 1 次付款后，所有未来的付款都可以自动支付。','With this enabled, the first name and last name fields will be required.'=>'启用此功能后，将需要名字和姓氏字段。','With this enabled, the link will be hidden for users that are not assigned to a coupon.'=>'启用此功能后，对于未分配给优惠券的用户，该链接将被隐藏。','With this enabled, the new user account created will be assigned to the default "Subscriber" role (or the custom role defined below) initially, and only when their affiliate application is accepted will they be assigned to the "coupon affiliate" user role instead.'=>'启用此功能后，创建的新用户帐户将最初分配到默认的"订阅者"角色（或下面定义的自定义角色），只有当其联盟应用程序被接受时，他们才会被分配到"优惠券联盟"用户角色。','With this enabled, the pending user role will be removed from the affiliate when the application is accepted.'=>'启用此功能后，当应用程序被接受时，待决用户角色将从联盟中删除。','With this enabled, the username field will be hidden, and the email address will be used as their username instead.'=>'启用此功能后，将隐藏用户名字段，并将电子邮件地址用作用户名。','With this enabled, when adding a new domain, affiliates will be able to select a "campaign" to assign that domains referrals to.'=>'启用此功能后，在添加新域时，联盟会员将能够选择要将该域的引荐分配给该域的"广告系列"。','With this enabled, when the "Affiliate" tab is clicked, instead of redirecting to the normal affiliate dashboard page, it will show the affiliate dashboard as a page/section within "My Account".'=>'启用此功能后，当单击“会员”选项卡时，它不会重定向到普通的会员仪表板页面，而是将会员仪表板显示为“我的帐户”中的页面/部分。','With this enabled, you will be able assign a user role to a template coupon, so when someone registers via that template option, they will also be assigned to this user role.'=>'启用此功能后，您将能够为模板优惠券分配用户角色，因此当有人通过该模板选项注册时，他们也将被分配给此用户角色。','With this feature, you can enable an option to prevent ALL affiliate coupons and referral links from working UNLESS the customer was directly linked by the approved domain that is assigned to that coupon.'=>'使用此功能，您可以启用一个选项来阻止所有优惠券和推荐链接正常工作，除非客户由分配给该优惠券的批准域直接链接。','WooCommerce coupons list'=>'伍商业优惠券列表','WooCommerce Subscriptions Settings'=>'伍商业订阅设置','WooCommerce Template'=>'WooCommerce 模板','WooCommerce Template (styled)'=>'WooCommerce 模板（已定型）','WooCommerce – Integration Guide'=>'伍商务 – 集成指南','WordPress Font Library'=>'WordPress 字体库','Would you like to set the new signup promo page as the default registration page?'=>'是否要将新的注册促销页面设置为默认注册页面？','Year (optional):'=>'年份（可选）：','Yes'=>'是的','Yes, you can view the dashboard for each of your affiliates\' coupons by going to the <a href="%s" target="_blank">coupons page</a> and click the "Dashboard" link.'=>'是的，您可以通过转到优惠券页面并单击“仪表板”链接来查看每个会员 <a href="%s" target="_blank">优惠券</a> 的仪表板。','You are all set! Store credit payouts can now be added to the users wallet automatically in one-click. They can spend this credit when visiting the cart/checkout.'=>'一切准备就绪！商店信用支出现在只需单击一下即可自动添加到用户钱包中。他们可以在访问购物车/结账时花费此积分。','You are all set! Store credit payouts will now be added to the users "%s" wallet automatically in one-click.'=>'一切准备就绪！现在，一键式将自动将商店信用支出添加到用户的"%s"钱包中。','You are already registered as an %s.'=>'您已经注册为联盟会员。','You are sending too many of requests in a short time and have been temporarily timed out.'=>'您在短时间内发送了太多的请求，并且已暂时中断。','You can <a href="%s" target="_blank">edit your template coupon</a> if you want to change the default affiliate coupon settings.'=>'如果您想更改默认的会员优惠券设置，您可以 <a href="%s" target="_blank">编辑模板优惠券</a> 。','You can adjust the horizontal and vertical margins to move the text around. The alignment of the text is centered.'=>'您可以调整水平和垂直边距以移动文本。文本的对齐方式居中。','You can also show the logged in affiliates default link anywhere using the shortcode: [couponaffiliates-referral-url]'=>'您还可以使用短代码在任何地方显示他们的默认链接：[couponaffiliates-referral-url]','You can also view a full list of the coupons, with the assigned user, pending payments, and unique affiliate dashboard links for each coupon (to view yourself) on the WooCommerce'=>'您还可以查看优惠券的完整列表，包括分配的用户，待处理的付款以及每个优惠券的唯一联盟仪表板链接（以查看自己）','You can apply additional strict fraud prevention with direct link tracking.'=>'您可以通过直接链接跟踪来应用其他严格的欺诈预防。','You can assign a group to an %s when adding or editing an %s.'=>'添加或编辑 %s 时，可以为 %s 指定组。','You can change the primary font used in the affiliate portal in the %s.'=>'您可以在 %s 中更改联盟门户网站使用的主要字体。','You can change the Registration Page in "Registration Settings" tab:'=>'您可以在 “Registration Settings” 选项卡中更改 Registration Page：','You can create groups here:'=>'您可以在此处创建组：','You can customise the affiliate portal more, including layout and colors, later on the settings page.'=>'您可以稍后在设置页面上对联盟门户进行更多自定义，包括布局和颜色。','You can customise the colors of the affiliate portal in the %s.'=>'您可以在 %s 中自定义联盟门户的颜色。','You can customise the content of the generated page template by modifying the fields below.'=>'您可以通过修改以下字段来自定义生成的页面模板的内容。','You can customise the form and add your own custom fields via the below settings.'=>'您可以通过以下设置自定义表单并添加自己的自定义字段。','You can customise the parent notification emails from the "Multi-Level Affiliate Emails" section in Email Notification settings.'=>'您可以在电子邮件通知设置中的 "多级联盟电子邮件 "部分自定义父级通知电子邮件。','You can customize the message displayed for the acceptance checkbox, during affiliate registration.'=>'在联属会员注册过程中，您可以自定义接受复选框显示的信息。','You can customize the plugin to meet your requirements on '=>'您可以自定义插件以满足您的要求','You can download MailPoet here:'=>'您可以在此处下载 MailPoet：','You can easily pay your affiliates via a variety of different payout methods including one-click Stripe, PayPal, or Store Credit, along with manual Bank Transfer payouts, or any custom manual payout method of your own. You can even automate payouts to be paid automatically on a scheduled basis, collect invoices, generate PDF statements, and more. <a href="%s" target="_blank">%s</a>'=>'您可以通过各种不同的收款方式轻松向您的会员付款，包括一键式 Stripe、PayPal 或商店信用，以及手动银行转账付款或您自己的任何自定义手动付款方式。您甚至可以自动付款以按计划自动支付、收集发票、生成 PDF 报表等。 <a href="%s" target="_blank">%s</a>','You can enable line graphs in the "Pro Settings" tab. This will show some nice line graphs on the statistics tab of the affiliate dashboard.'=>'您可以在"专业设置"选项卡中启用折线图。这将在联盟仪表板的统计信息选项卡上显示一些漂亮的折线图。','You can enable referral URLs, and customise the settings for these, in the "Referral Links" tab on the settings tab.'=>'您可以在设置页面上的"转介网网"选项卡中启用转介网点，并自定义这些设置。','You can enable the "Scheduled Payouts" feature, which will schedule payout requests to be submitted on a regular basis.'=>'您可以启用“定期提现”功能，该功能将安排定期提交提现请求。','You can get your API key from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取您的 API 密钥：','You can get your API URL from your ActiveCampaign dashboard: Account > Settings > Developer'=>'您可以从 ActiveCampaign 控制面板获取 API URL：Account > Settings > Developer','You can get your Audience ID from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取受众 ID：','You can get your Contact List ID from here:'=>'您可以从这里获取联系人列表 ID：','You can get your Form ID from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取 Form ID：','You can get your List ID from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取您的列表 ID：','You can get your List ID from your ActiveCampaign dashboard: Contacts > Lists > Click on the list > View the ID in the URL ("listid").'=>'您可以从 ActiveCampaign 控制面板获取您的列表 ID：联系人>列表 > 单击列表>查看 URL 中的 ID（“listid”）。','You can get your List Token from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取 List Token：','You can get your private API key from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取您的私有 API 密钥：','You can get your site key and secret key from here:'=>'您可以从此处获取站点密钥和密钥：','You can however customise this below if required:'=>'但是，如果需要，您可以在下面进行自定义：','You can manage the user roles/groups that are assigned to the template coupons in the "Registrations" settings tab of the Coupon Affiliates settings.'=>'您可以在 Coupon Affiliates 设置的 “Registrations” 设置选项卡中管理分配给模板优惠券的用户角色/组。','You can manually create an affiliate by <a href="%s" target="_blank">clicking here</a>.<br/><br/>You can add either an existing or new user. Alternatively, you can also link users to your <a href="%s" target="_blank">affiliate registration page</a> to submit an affiliate application. When an affiliate user is added, this will automatically create the affiliate coupon, assign the user to it, and send them a link to the affiliate dashboard. <a href="%s" target="_blank">Learn more about affiliate registration.</a>'=>'您可以 <a href="%s" target="_blank">点击此处</a>手动创建会员。<br/><br/>您可以添加现有用户或新用户。或者，您也可以将用户链接到您的会员 <a href="%s" target="_blank">注册页面</a> 以提交会员申请。添加会员用户后，这将自动创建会员优惠券，将用户分配给该优惠券，并向他们发送指向会员仪表板的链接。 <a href="%s" target="_blank">详细了解联盟注册。</a>','You can now give access to the MLA Dashboard for specific affiliate users. To do this, edit the user and enable "MLA Dashboard Access".'=>'您现在可以为特定附属用户授予对 MLA 仪表板的访问权限。为此，请编辑用户并启用“MLA Dashboard Access”。','You can set fixed commission amounts (either per order, or per product), alongside percentage of the total order. You can set all 3 of these for a combined total if required.'=>'您可以设置固定佣金金额（每个订单或每个产品），以及总订单的百分比。如果需要，您可以将所有这些 3 个组合为总和。','You can set the global commission rates for all coupons in the <a href="%s">plugin settings</a> page.'=>'您可以在 <a href="%s">插件设置</a> 页面中设置所有优惠券的全球佣金率。','You can set your custom commission rates in the "commission" tab of the'=>'您可以在"通信"选项卡中设置您的自定义佣金率','You can then customise the the page further after it is generated, by editing the page itself.'=>'然后，您可以在页面生成后通过编辑页面本身来进一步自定义页面。','You can track and manage payouts on the'=>'您可以跟踪和管理支出','You can update the tier 1 affiliate (who invited this user). All other tiers will be updated automatically based on that affiliates network.'=>'您可以更新第 1 层联盟（邀请此用户的人）。所有其他级别将根据该联盟网络自动更新。','You can use the terms and conditions manager and generation tool to help you easily create your terms and conditions page.'=>'您可以使用条款和条件管理器和生成工具来帮助您轻松创建条款和条件页面。','You can view, edit and accept the application below.'=>'您可以在下方查看、编辑并接受申请。','You cannot clone instances of %s.'=>'您不能克隆%s 实例。','You cannot unserialize instances of %s.'=>'您不能取消对 %s 实例的去美化。','You currently have no %s!'=>'您目前没有 %s！','You currently have scheduled payouts enabled. This will automatically submit payout requests for all affiliates with more than'=>'您当前已启用定期提现。这将自动为超过','You do not have permission to access the affiliate portal.'=>'您没有访问联盟门户网站的权限。','You do not have permission to access this data.'=>'您无权访问这些数据。','You do not have permission to action this registration.'=>'您没有进行此注册的权限。','You do not have sufficient permissions to access this page.'=>'您没有足够的权限访问此页面。','You do not have sufficient permissions.'=>'您没有足够的权限。','You don\'t currently have any sub-affiliates.'=>'您目前#39t有任何子关联公司。','You don\'t currently have any sub-affiliates. Use the Invite tab to invite new members to your network.'=>'您目前没有任何次级会员。使用 "邀请 "选项卡邀请新成员加入您的网络。','You don\'t have any active %s coupons right now.'=>'您现在没有任何有效的 %s 优惠券。','You don\'t have any completed commission payments yet.'=>'您还没有完成任何佣金付款。','You don\'t have any processing commission payments.'=>'您没有任何待定的佣金付款。','You have a pending %s application.'=>'你已有一个待处理的关联应用程序。','You have a Pro license! Please deactivate the FREE version and install the PRO version instead to enable the new functionality.'=>'您拥有专业版许可证！请停用免费版本并安装PRO版本以启用新功能。','You have been unsubscribed from affiliate newsletters.'=>'您已退订联盟通讯。','You have earned a reward!'=>'您已经获得了奖励！','You have made a new referral sale!'=>'您已经进行了新的推荐销售！','You have no %s yet.'=>'您还没有 %。','you have no pending %s registrations.'=>'您没有待处理的联属会员注册。','You have no pending payout requests.'=>'您没有待处理的付款申请。','You must be logged in to perform this action.'=>'您必须登录后才能执行此操作。','You must be logged in to view the MLA dashboard.'=>'您必须登录才能查看 MLA 仪表板。','You must be logged in to view this.'=>'您必须登录后才能查看。','You must be logged in.'=>'您必须已登录。','You must provide one of the following: IBAN, UK Sort Code + Account Number, US Routing Number + Account Number, or SWIFT Code + Account Number.'=>'您必须提供以下信息之一：IBAN、UK Sort Code + Account Number、US Routing Number + Account Number 或 SWIFT Code + Account Number。','You need to be logged in to view your bonuses.'=>'您需要登录后才能查看您的奖金。','You should only disable this if your primary method of tracking referrals is through customers manually applying the affiliates coupon at checkout.'=>'仅当您跟踪推荐的主要方法是通过客户在结账时手动应用联盟优惠券时，您才应禁用此功能。','You will be able to customise more group settings once it has been added.'=>'添加后，您将能够自定义更多群组设置。','You will be able to customise more options in the <a href="%s" target="_blank">settings page</a> later.'=>'稍后，您将能够在 <a href="%s">设置页面中</a> 自定义更多选项。','You will just need to use the shortcode:'=>'您只需要使用短代码：','You will still be able to review and edit the generated code before approving.'=>'在批准之前，您仍然可以查看和编辑生成的代码。','You\'re almost ready to launch your affiliate program, and start growing your revenue!'=>'您几乎已经准备好启动您的联盟计划，并开始增加您的收入！','Your %s application for the coupon code "{coupon}" has been submitted.'=>'您的 %s 优惠券代码"{coupon}"申请已提交。','Your %s application has been submitted.'=>'您的联盟申请已提交。','Your Account'=>'您的帐户','Your affiliate network:'=>'您的联盟网络：','Your affiliate portal will be located at:'=>'您的联属会员门户网站将位于','Your Affiliate Program signup promo page has been created. You can update it or view it below.'=>'您的联盟计划注册促销页面已创建。您可以更新它或在下面查看它。','Your affiliate statistics need to be refreshed and recalculated. Please visit your full affiliate dashboard to complete this process.'=>'您的联属会员统计数据需要刷新和重新计算。请访问您的联属会员控制面板完成此过程。','Your affiliate users can manage and manually submit their own payout by visiting the "Payouts" tab on their affiliate dashboard.'=>'您的联盟用户可以通过访问其联盟仪表板上的“付款”选项卡来管理和手动提交自己的付款。','Your Commission'=>'您的佣金','Your Coupon'=>'您的优惠券','Your Coupon Code'=>'您的优惠券代码','Your latest invites:'=>'您的最新邀请：','Your MLA Commission Rates'=>'您的工作重点佣金率','Your PRO license is not active. Access to some PRO features may now be limited. Please <a href=\'%s\'>active your license</a>, or <a href=\'%s\'>upgrade again</a> to enable PRO features.'=>'您的专业版许可证未激活。某些专业功能的访问现在可能受到限制。请激活您的许可证，或再次升级以启用专业版功能。','Your profile picture is managed via Gravatar. To set or change it, visit '=>'您的个人资料图片通过 Gravatar 管理。要设置或更改它，请访问','Your referred order #{id} has been cancelled.'=>'您推荐的订单 #{id} 已被取消。','Your sub-affiliate coupons:'=>'您的子联盟优惠券：','Your sub-affiliates don\'t have any active coupons yet.'=>'您的次级会员还没有任何有效优惠券。','Your users can become super-affiliates and invite other affiliates to be a part of their network. They will then earn extra commission from all their referrals.'=>'您的用户可以成为超级联盟会员，并邀请其他会员成为其网络的一部分。然后，他们将从所有推荐中获得额外的佣金。','Your Website'=>'您的网站','YouTube URL:'=>'优酷网址：','Youtube Video'=>'Youtube 视频','Zoom In'=>'放大','{number} New Payout Requests'=>'[编号]新的支付请求','• Paid: Successfully paid to affiliate.'=>'- 已支付：成功支付给联属会员。','• Pending: Payout requests currently awaiting approval.'=>'- 待定：目前正在等待批准的付款申请。','• Unpaid: Earned from completed orders but not yet paid.'=>'- 未付款：已完成订单但尚未支付的收入。','• Unpaid: MLA commission earned but not yet paid.'=>'- 未支付：已赚取但尚未支付的工作重点佣金。','✓ SMS sent successfully!'=>'✓ 短信发送成功！','✓ This page is currently set as the default registration Page.'=>'✓ 此页面当前设置为默认注册页面。','✗ Error: '=>'✗ 错误：','✗ Request failed.'=>'✗ 请求失败。']];
